msgctxt "Content/2084549226"
msgid ""
"A woman named Helena arrived at my camp yesterday, though not to hire me. She "
"said that she was a scholar studying the creatures on this island, and that "
"she wanted to observe my beasts. I turned her away at first, not trusting her "
"intentions. How could I? What mad fool would bother with scholarly pursuits "
"in a place like this? Yet she persisted, and in time I was convinced of her "
"honesty.\n"
"\n"
