msgctxt "Content/3221413509"
msgid ""
"ABERRATION:\n"
"Waking up on Aberration, a derelict, malfunctioning ARK with an elaborate "
"underground biome system, survivors face exotic new challenges unlike "
"anything before: extreme radioactive sunlight and environmental hazards, "
"ziplines, wingsuits, climbing gear, cave dwellings, charge-batteries, and far "
"more, along with a stable of extraordinary new creatures await within the "
"mysterious depths. But beware the 'Nameless': unrelenting, Element-infused "
"humanoids which have evolved into vicious light-hating monstrosities! On "
"Aberration, survivors will uncover the ultimate secrets of the ARKs, and "
"discover what the future holds in store for those strong and clever enough to "
"survive!"
msgstr ""

