msgctxt "Content/1757860402"
msgid ""
"According to the maps, we are nearing the tomb's location. I have made short "
"work of the monsters and disfigured beasts that have stood in our way, and "
"the path ahead seems clear. However something looms behind us, growing ever "
"closer.\n"
"\n"
"It's another horde, and while it lacks the mountainous demon that attacked us "
"before, there are other, lesser devils in its place. Though smaller than "
"their master, they are still far larger than any normal beast, and their "
"might will be considerable.\n"
"\n"
"Fortunately, my pack is outpacing them. We should arrive at the tomb well "
"ahead of the horde, and if I can heal Helena quickly, we may be able to avoid "
"it all together."
msgstr ""

