msgstr ""

msgctxt "Content/3665633909"
msgid ""
"Again and again, the monsters come. It seems as though there is no end to "
"their number, but I know that cannot be true. I must keep fighting.\n"
"\n"
"Yet as time passes, that grows far more difficult to do. One by one my beasts "
"are falling, and I can only rest at times like these, in the gaps between "
"assaults. My eyelids are heavy, my muscles sore and only writing like this is "
"keeping my mind from growing hazy.\n"
"\n"
"The gigantic demons still stand idle, letting their lessers wear down my "
"forces so they can strike me when I am at my weakest. Yet they cannot wait "
"forever, for the tomb continues to rumble below. Eventually their patience "
"will run out, and in that moment, this battle will be decided."
msgstr ""

