msgctxt "Content/3032675226"
msgid ""
"Alas, poor Timur. He was so focused on celebrating his victory over one foe, "
"that he never saw his greatest threat. Now he lies beneath the severed head "
"of the beast he vanquished, eyes bulging and blood seeping from his open "
"mouth.\n"
"\n"
"At least, that is how I imagine him. I did not stay to admire my handiwork. "
"As soon as the first group of Burning Phoenix warriors succumbed to their "
"poisoned feast, I stole away into the night, Edmunium and artifact in "
"tow.\n"
"\n"
"Serves those ruffians right, I say! They never did treat me with the "
"propriety that a gentleman and scholar of my caliber deserves. This desert is "
"better off without them."
msgstr ""

