msgctxt "Content/931062915"
msgid ""
"Any thought of those images being hallucinations evaporated when Kazuma came "
"back from his scouting run this morning. An army of monsters is headed our "
"way, and I don't think it's a coincidence.\n"
"\n"
"They're after the prism, that has to be it. So if I get rid of it...no, I "
"don't think that will work. Those monsters won't stop with the prism, they'll "
"devour everyone who came into contact with it. Somehow I just get that "
"feeling.\n"
"\n"
"Ugh, why am I only getting visions of how doomed we are? Show me something I "
"can do to save my friends, you lambent little bludger!\n"
"\n"
"Damn it all. Maybe I'll think of something once we're on the move. For now, "
"we've got to get the hell out of here."
msgstr ""

