msgctxt "Content/2372873564"
msgid ""
"Astounding! That remarkable armor was but the tip of the iceberg. The "
"barbarian woman has escorted us to the home of her new masters, and I can "
"take nary a step without finding some wondrous new piece of technology - much "
"of it relying on the power of Edmundium.\n"
"The casual manner in which they use and refer to these wonders leads me to "
"believe that while they are deeply familiar with the marvelous metal, they "
"may not grasp the depths of its potential.\n"
"Yes, Rockwell, this was well worth tolerating Miss Walker and her savage "
"companion. I shall learn what these supposed \"future men\" know, and take it "
"many steps further."
msgstr ""

