msgctxt "Content/1089953037"
msgid ""
"Back in Luxor, I always tried to stay out of politics. I never aspired to be "
"Divine Adoratrice as some priestesses did. I found that such selfish "
"ambitions often led to suffering – both for oneself and for others.\n"
"\n"
"So when Girisha referred to me as our leader today, I found myself surprised. "
"I had never asked for such a position, and the others had never bestowed it "
"on me in any official manner. It just happened naturally.\n"
"\n"
"I am not sure what to make of it, but if this is Hathor's will, then I will "
"try to guide these people as best as I can."
msgstr ""

