msgctxt "Content/2906701998"
msgid ""
"By daylight I fumed at myself for running off on my own.\n"
"\n"
"My pride and stubborn self-reliance has only ever brought me ruination.\n"
"\n"
"I turned my stryder back toward where I'd left Nida, near the edges of this "
"wheel.\n"
"\n"
"I set aside my own desire to recover the mineral wealth I had lost once, and "
"my half-memories of a previous life's pursuit of power.\n"
"\n"
"There was only this moment, and this chance to do something right, for once "
"in my miserable existence.\n"
"\n"
"I pushed the machine to its breaking point, urging it into a full gallop "
"toward the girl I'd abandoned to an unfair fight.\n"
"\n"
"As I re-crossed that landscape shame gnawed at me, for the way I'd reacted to "
"the dream she'd painted for me.\n"
"\n"
"She'd only wanted to show me a sunset on the world I was destined to tame, "
"far from these gardens she and her people had kept alive for a future they "
"never thought they'd see."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "Content/2593591638"
msgid ""
"By now, Mei-Yin and I can understand each other with only a handful of words. "
"I just said I was sorry for being short with her, and that was that. She "
"knows how much this means to me, and I know that she's just wants to protect "
"me, even from myself.\n"
"\n"
"I even told her about the images I'm seeing. She dismissed them as nonsense, "
"but I'm not so sure. They're growing clearer with every day I spend studying "
"the prism, and one in particular keeps coming up.\n"
"\n"
"In it, I see a single room, in the depths of a cave. It is both a tomb and a "
"throne - where a coffin like structure sits on a raised platform, surrounded "
"by silvery metal and glowing crystals. The walls glimmer and a light shines "
"down from above, or is it rising up from below? I can't tell.\n"
"\n"
"What does it mean? Anything at all? Or do I really just need to get more "
"sleep?"
msgstr ""

