msgctxt "Content/2066502106"
msgid ""
"Cause and effect is the way of the universe. Everything must start somewhere. "
"In the case of the System, this is where it was born. You will fall right "
"into its cradle.\n"
"\n"
"Together, the sanctuaries and the Obelisks that power them are the ancestor "
"of every island that floats in the sky. They can all can trace their origins "
"back to this single prototype. Though it is flightless, the core principles "
"and technology behind it are the same.\n"
"\n"
"In a way, that makes it your ancestor too. You were all born within the "
"System, after all. Even if your design is somewhat altered, in a way, you're "
"all its children.\n"
"\n"
"One could say that when you fall, it will be something of a homecoming. In "
"more ways than one."
msgstr ""

