msgctxt "Content/1393689004"
msgid ""
"Controlling this armored giant has grown easier, but it will never feel "
"familiar. Though its limbs move as mine do, that is in itself disquieting, "
"and sometimes I get lost in the flashing lights that surround me. \n"
"\n"
"Helena is far more attuned to her giant's abilities than I am, though as in "
"all things, she underestimates herself. Ever since I cast that monstrous old "
"man into the depths, she's been there to pull me back. Not just from the "
"fall, but the abyss itself.\n"
"\n"
"I will still never understand why she was so interested in studying animal "
"excrement when we first met, but after walking this path with her, I can "
"recognize the strength of her spirit. I will do all I can to protect it."
msgstr ""

