msgctxt "Content/1910027136"
msgid ""
"Damn it all to hell! I had everything under control. We were going to make "
"it, but I just had to go searching for that town. What a stupid, bone-headed "
"decision! \n"
"\n"
"It's not that the rumor was wrong. There are buildings, all right: crumbling, "
"abandoned buildings that are half-buried in sand...and home to a group of "
"damned wyverns that attacked us on the way in. We managed to give them the "
"slip by taking shelter in this big, circular building, but they've been "
"circling it ever since. \n"
"\n"
"We've got enough supplies for nearly a week. Hopefully they'll lose interest "
"before we start to run dry."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "Content/826374509"
msgid ""
"Damn these barbarians. They've smelled our weakness.\n"
"\n"
"Between our battles with the Beast Queen and the dragon, the New Legion's "
"main army has been distracted and depleted. Lesser tribes have taken "
"advantage by raiding our camps and seizing territory that we claimed with our "
"blood and sweat.\n"
"\n"
"Fine. Let them have their temporary victories. Let them imagine that they "
"have inflicted real wounds upon us. When I obtain the power of the obelisks, "
"they will pay for every blade of grass they take from me. With that power, I "
"will make them know true regret.\n"
"\n"
"Gaius Marcellus Nerva\n"
"Victoria per Disciplinam"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "Content/1465922723"
msgid ""
"Damn those New Legion cowards! At full strength, I could have fended them "
"off, but they attacked just as we returned to the pillar of light. What "
"beasts I had were exhausted, and the Demon King flew into a rage before I "
"could start a retreat. When that happened, all hope was lost.\n"
"\n"
"The last thing I remember is a sharp pain in my side. When I awoke, I was "
"alone with Wuzhui. Both of us were covered in blood, but Wuzhui's wounds were "
"deeper. I cannot fathom how he carried me to safety in such a state.\n"
"\n"
"I must find a place to hide. Wuzhui and I are alone now, and barely clinging "
"to hope."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "Content/60743164"
msgid ""
"Damn! I should've calculated for this possibility.\n"
"Must've...missed a transform on the 15th statistical outcome matrix..."
msgstr ""

