msgctxt "Content/1782038776"
msgid ""
"Desert Titan\n"
"\n"
"The Lord of Sand and Sky has fallen, despite its swarms of protectors, the "
"powerful swings of its mighty tail or the lightning it called from the sky. "
"The soaring leviathan could not match the ingenuity of humanity, and "
"especially not yours."
