msgctxt "Content/523171438"
msgid ""
"Folks have been spotting a lot more of these wyvern creatures, and they're "
"not just throwing fire every which way, either. Some spit lightning or acid. "
"\n"
"\n"
"On top of that, those big pillars are acting funny. I checked with Sasha, "
"since she doesn't buy into that Hathor business, and she sees it too. It's "
"making me restless. Between this and the mantises, it's starting to feel like "
"this place wants us gone.\n"
"\n"
"I know that can't be right. There were no spirits of the land to stop the "
"frontiersman back home, and there are none here. Still, I should talk to "
"Raia. If that tower's dangerous, she shouldn't be worshipping it."
msgstr ""

