msgctxt "Content/4139048179"
msgid ""
"How can these tribal leaders be so short sighted? Yes, the members of their "
"respective tribes who volunteered for my Battle Tartare and Shadow Steak "
"Sauté experiments have been experiencing prolonged withdrawal episodes, but "
"can't they see that the benefits outweigh the costs? I created mixtures that "
"can bring out superhuman strength, speed and coordination in ordinary men and "
"they can only focus on the negatives. Simple minded, the lot of "
"them!\n"
"\n"
"They've even banned their members from partaking in my experiments now. "
"Ridiculous! I'll not let them stand in the way of human progress. They may "
"not understand the importance of my work, but surely my assistants do."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "Content/425774111"
msgid "How clumsy. How… pathetic."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "Content/2246213225"
msgid ""
"How could ones such as my elders decay like they did? I once asked the same "
"question, but no longer. No one told me the answer. I have simply felt it as "
"I wait, bearing down on me, bit by bit.\n"
"\n"
"Think, how much have you ever seen at once? Were you able to process it all, "
"to take in every little detail? Now imagine doing that for two such images. "
"Now a hundred. A thousand. Ten thousand. A million.\n"
"\n"
"All that knowledge, all that information, flows into us. It's what let my "
"elders build the System. It's what let me grant you your name, One Who Tries "
"Again, and it's what lets me speak to you now.\n"
"\n"
"Yet inevitably, our minds crumble beneath the weight of all that truth, and "
"our souls? They turn to smoke."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "Content/2277834062"
msgid ""
"How could ones such as my elders decay like they did? I once asked the same "
"question, but no longer. No one told me the answer. I have simply felt it as "
"I wait, bearing down on me, bit by bit.\n"
"\n"
"Think, how much have you ever seen at once? Were you able to process it all, "
"to take in every little detail? Now imagine doing that for two such images. "
"Now a hundred. A thousand. Ten thousand. A million.\n"
"\n"
"All that knowledge, all that information, flows into us. It's what let my "
"elders build the System. It's what let me grant you your name, One Who Tries "
"Again, and it's what lets me speak to you now.\n"
"\n"
"Yet inevitably, our minds crumble beneath the weight of all that truth, and "
"our souls? They turn to smoke."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "Content/1161129865"
msgid ""
"How do Trent and Imamu stay so motivated? The other day, we built a series of "
"ziplines to help us get around, and it felt like they did all the heavy "
"lifting, even though I'm the engineering student. Compared to them, I've done "
"next to nothing since Rusty disappeared.\n"
"\n"
"I'm not even good at sleeping anymore. I wake up at every sound, afraid that "
"those wolf creatures we spotted might tear through our makeshift shelter and "
"devour us. It's all I can think about, all the different ways we could die "
"and all the ways it'd be my fault.\n"
"\n"
"Ugh, being such a burden on everyone is the grossest feeling ever. So why "
"can't I do anything about it?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "Content/1829932694"
msgid ""
