msgctxt "Content/3265122282"
msgid ""
"How long have I wanted this? I can't place it exactly, but it feels like I "
"always have. I suppose that's how I know it's right.\n"
"\n"
"It's not just that Raia's beautiful. I've known beautiful women before, but I "
"never got the same feeling when I looked at them. I never felt this at home "
"around them, or anyone for that matter. What happened between us when I was "
"stuck in that room, it wasn't a heat of the moment decision. At least I don't "
"think.\n"
"\n"
"All I know is that now, I don't mind sleeping in the same bed every night. "
"Not anymore."
msgstr ""

