msgctxt "Content/3375515182"
msgid ""
"If nothing else, my own sessions have been a moment of peace. I still don't "
"want to pilot one of my own masterpieces in combat, but when it's just me and "
"my MEK in the hangar, I feel like I can finally relax.\n"
"\n"
"It's not just that I've been working long hours. I did that plenty of times "
"on the Gateway Project, and our TEK bomb before then. It's that I'm working "
"long hours and dealing with people at the same time, all the time. The pilot "
"sessions have been getting better, but running everything else on top of "
"that?\n"
"\n"
"\"Santiago, a water pipe broke. Santiago, so and so is hogging all the "
"ammo.\" Constant interruptions.\n"
"\n"
"Maybe I'll just hide in the cockpit and nap for a while. No one would know..."
msgstr ""

