msgctxt "Content/1149388659"
msgid ""
"Li Mei-Yin, the Beast Queen of the Jungle. That is the name of my foe. It is "
"a name that I have already grown weary of, but soon I will never hear it "
"again.\n"
"\n"
"It turns out that she is a mercenary not beholden to any tribe, including the "
"Painted Sharks. So as satisfying as it may be, I need not actually defeat "
"her. I must simply divorce her from her employers, and I know exactly how to "
"do it. The seeds of my victory are already planted.\n"
"\n"
"Gaius Marcellus Nerva\n"
"Victoria per Disciplinam"
msgstr ""

