msgctxt "Content/2410768332"
msgid ""
"Lost souls from all across the desert continue to prostrate themselves before "
"Nosti's gates. I adamantly refuse to turn away anyone that does not mean us "
"any harm, but I realize that has left us with many mouths to feed.\n"
"\n"
"As a result, Nosti's fields are its most valuable asset. Fortunately, "
"Girisha's designs and my organization of labor and resources have once again "
"proven effective. Not only did we implement an efficient irrigation system, "
"but we have encased our crops in a large, protective structure made of a "
"clear, shiny substance called \"glass.\"\n"
"\n"
"Every morning, it sparkles with Amun-Ra's light like a great gem, a beautiful "
"reminder of what we can accomplish when we are united in purpose."
msgstr ""

