msgctxt "Content/111295857"
msgid ""
"Maybe I should change my name again. Seems fitting. I started calling myself "
"John about a week after joining up with Doc Russo. The others never called me "
"Dahkeya anyway, so I figured they may as well call me by a name I chose "
"myself. \n"
"\n"
"That was part of it, but I think that deep down, I also knew that the boy who "
"earned the name Dahkeya was gone for good. Now I think the outlaw named John "
"Dahkeya is gone too, so it would make sense to call myself something "
"else.\n"
"\n"
"Then again, that may just confuse folks. Probably not worth the hassle. "
"Besides, I kind of like the way it sounds with an Egyptian accent."
msgstr ""

