msgctxt "Content/3113639973"
msgid ""
"Miss Walker I can tolerate for now, but I cannot abide by this barbarian!\n"
"I cannot fathom how she even lives, much less how she ended up here! A "
"primitive mind like hers could never have operated the contraptions in the "
"starlit sanctuary. Yet here she stands, and worst of all, she wears a suit of "
"Edmundium armor! The very thing I seek has already been claimed by some "
"savage, sword wielding tart!\n"
"It's outrageous! Such a beautiful product of science should not be sullied by "
"her\n"
"bloodstained hands. No, Rockwell. You must be calm. If she senses hostility, "
"she will surely kill you on the spot.\n"
"Yes, for now I must bide my time and learn what I can. Whoever constructed "
"this armor, I must find them."
msgstr ""

