msgctxt "Content/3320191008"
msgid ""
"Most of my work work as the monastery's doctor has been trivial. Every now "
"and then one of the guards gets injured by the local wildlife, but I usually "
"find myself treating heat stroke and common illnesses. As such, I have had "
"plenty of time to learn all the priests know about the obelisks.\n"
"\n"
"All told, they are stunningly ill informed about the literal pillars of their "
"faith. They are unaware that the obelisks are actually devices that can be "
"activated, and needless to say they have never activated one "
"themselves.\n"
"\n"
"They showed a flicker of understanding when I described the artifacts I found "
"on the Island, however. I shall have to keep digging."
msgstr ""

