msgctxt "Content/1201965656"
msgid ""
"Navigating the forest has been easier with Xiao at my side. His light has "
"both guided and protected me. The small, spined monsters that I fought before "
"returned in numbers, but they cowered and fled before Xiao's light, as they "
"did from the glowing pillar. So long as Xiao is with me, I need not fear "
"them.\n"
"Yet Xiao's power is not an endless well. If he does not periodically "
"extinguish his light to rest, it will fade with time on its own. I must be "
"careful when wandering into the darkest parts of this forest, lest Xiao's "
"light go out and we are both put at risk."
msgstr ""

