msgctxt "Content/1462828239"
msgid ""
"Near dark, the girl was excited to show me something.\n"
"\n"
"She'd pried open one of her hidden doors and pressed her magic device against "
"the machinery inside.\n"
"\n"
"I didn't follow what she tried to explain to me next...\n"
"\n"
"Nida said I was wired to connect to a sort of game she'd made, from my time "
"in the shadowland she called Genesis.\n"
"\n"
"Then she did something, and all at once I was on another world, in a new "
"body.\n"
"\n"
"There were no wheels overhead, only a setting sun scudded with clouds.\n"
"\n"
"I struggled to understand-had I ever truly been in Nida's sky-garden?\n"
"\n"
"I called to her, but instead heard the voice of the angel I'd met in "
"Purgatory.\n"
"\n"
"The angel told me something important.\n"
"\n"
"Then I was yanked back into reality, if this was actually reality.\n"
"\n"
"Nida grinned at me and asked what I thought, and I got sick all over the "
"canyon floor."
msgstr ""

