msgctxt "Content/3243550197"
msgid ""
"News of my rather definitive response to the Arrows' proposal has spread "
"quickly, but few seem keen to act on it. Who can blame them? Without their "
"leaders, the Arrows quickly folded, and the New Legion grew significantly in "
"power practically overnight.\n"
"\n"
"The other tribes only managed to interrupt their cowering long enough to send "
"another envoy, a man named Edmund Rockwell. Given the results of the last one "
"I received, I almost didn't believe it, but apparently this man is special. "
"The other tribes seem to respect him as a neutral party and expert on the "
"island. We shall see.\n"
"\n"
"Gaius Marcellus Nerva\n"
"Victoria per Disciplinam"
msgstr ""

