msgctxt "Content/1797551828"
msgid ""
"Nida stood at the feet of the colossal four-legged machines, and fiddled with "
"some device in her hand.\n"
"\n"
"One of the stryders dipped its head toward the ground and I made a fool of "
"myself by jumping in front of her.\n"
"\n"
"Even though I knew it was a machine, I'd still half-expected it to snatch her "
"up in its metal jaws to eat her alive.\n"
"\n"
"She shook her head at me with a smirk, and then she turned to grab handholds "
"to haul herself up onto its neck.\n"
"\n"
"From there, she was able to scramble up onto its back, where a sort of saddle "
"platform folded into place seemingly from nowhere for her to stand "
"on.\n"
"\n"
"After a moment, the second stryder dropped its head for my benefit, but I "
"opted to follow the girl up to where she was standing on the first one.\n"
"\n"
"It seemed wiser to learn from her how to tame and ride these behemoths before "
"attempting it myself."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "Content/145438140"
msgid ""
"Nida's been training me on the workings of the stryders wandering the gardens "
"above us.\n"
"\n"
"She says they follow their own will but we can break them like gigantic wild "
"mules, and use them to storm the other wheel.\n"
"\n"
"I try to remind myself she's a clever girl from a time long after my own, but "
"still it irritates me when she talks down to me as if I’m some niño "
"tonto.\n"
"\n"
"Maybe that's why I'm not convinced that I need to help fight her invader. "
"\n"
"\n"
"On the other hand, I sat out the war to defend the ranchos of Alta California "
"from Anglo invaders, and those malparidos ended up killing me for my "
"property.\n"
"\n"
"I have here a rare chance to revenge myself on an occupying force, even if I "
"have no claim to these gardens or their mineral wealth.\n"
"\n"
"Maybe I can earn a larger plot of land on whatever world we eventually "
"settle..."
msgstr ""

