msgctxt "Content/3284177516"
msgid ""
"Nothing! How can there be nothing? I have searched ceaselessly, and yet I "
"find NOTHING!\n"
"\n"
"I sacrificed my men, my kingdom, everything. I have nothing left to give. "
"Everything I've bled for is gone! For what? For a view?\n"
"\n"
"What trickery is this? What is this place? Am I the victim of some divine "
"joke? I don't understand. I served the Emperor loyally. Why would Janus pull "
"me from his service if not to bring order here? \n"
"\n"
"I've cried out for answers, but the gods never respond. They have abandoned "
"me. All I hear is my own voice, echoing off these cursed halls – betrayed, "
"destitute and alone."
msgstr ""

