msgctxt "Content/443713369"
msgid ""
"Okay, I've calmed down.\n"
"\n"
"Hurt feelings aside, I'd never do anything to risk this project-I've totally "
"bought into our mission here.\n"
"\n"
"I’ve spent too much of my life breaking things, and it matters to me that "
"I've been given this chance to make amends.\n"
"\n"
"I owe it to my species to try to help us escape extinction.\n"
"\n"
"If our shot at survival means I have to swallow my dumb pride, then it's no "
"contest.\n"
"\n"
"I'm only human-more or less.\n"
"\n"
"They cloned me against my will and gave me a bunch of fake memories to cover "
"that up, but supposedly because they needed me to be a part of this.\n"
"\n"
"Uma more or less said I was a natural leader, so that has to count for "
"something.\n"
"\n"
"Maybe I actually envy my transhuman benefactors a little...\n"
"\n"
"It must be great to be able to set aside all their feelings and really focus "
"on what it's going to take to save the world."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "Content/1431982675"
msgid ""
"Okay, it's done. I've managed to slave the legs, head and left arm to my "
"controls. Mei's better than me at hand-to-hand, so she'll still pilot the "
"sword arm, but anything more than that would overwhelm her with information "
"and technological complexity. \n"
"\n"
"In other words, when we enter combat, I'm going to assume control of 75% of "
"the MegaMEK's systems. It'll be a mental and physical strain, but I'm "
"prepared to take it. Like I said, it's my turn to carry the load, and I'm in "
"my wheelhouse here. If there's anyone who can handle this, it's me. Not like "
"there's time for another plan anyway - the titan's almost here.\n"
"\n"
"All right you ugly son of a bitch, let's go!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "Content/1071484738"
