msgctxt "Content/772962475"
msgid ""
"Old habits die hard. I suppose I'm living proof.\n"
"\n"
"I woke up stark naked who knows where with who knows what lodged in my arm, "
"but just weeks later and I'm already back to robbing folks at gunpoint. This "
"place may not be Texas or the Arizona Territory, but I'm the same John "
"Dahkeya.\n"
"\n"
"I don't know why that makes me restless. I didn't mind this life before, but "
"then I didn't exactly choose it. I just stumbled into it, or at least that's "
"what I told myself. So much for that. Maybe this is just who I am."
msgstr ""

