msgctxt "Content/2355633323"
msgid ""
"Perri started in with another sermon about our sacred mission today when she "
"found me modeling creature behavior for my latest sim.\n"
"\n"
"I tried to explain that I was on break, that I wasn't doing anything wrong, "
"but she wouldn't hear it.\n"
"\n"
"As if I haven't had it drilled into my head over and over that the survival "
"of all life from our homeworld depends on our sacred efforts...\n"
"\n"
"I work as hard as anyone on the ship, so why do I keep getting shamed for "
"having a hobby?\n"
"It's not like a half-cycle spent away from soil sampling is going to "
"jeopardize humanity's hopes of re-establishing itself on a new "
"planet.\n"
"\n"
"Besides, I know from the server logs that Perri played my last sim along with "
"most of the crew.\n"
"\n"
"What's wrong with dipping out off-shift and immersing yourself in some "
"harmless escapism?"
msgstr ""

