"Journey through an expansive 144 sq. kilometer fantasty highland, where "
"common and all-new biomes are combined to bring the ultimate survivor "
"experience. Whether tackling the extreme cold atop the highest mountains, "
"harvesting resources from an active volcano, or just searching for that "
"perfect base location, Ragnarok plays host to explorers and base builders "
"alike. But survivors beware, Ragnarok houses such creatures as Polar Bears, "
"Ice Wyverns, and a mystical creature many have yet to tame in the ARK "
"universe."
msgstr ""

