msgctxt "Content/3261319549"
msgid ""
"Remarkable! Absolutely remarkable! When I chose that remote northern cave as "
"the site of my spectacular spelunking sojourn, I'd never imagined that I'd "
"find such wonders within. Granted, I don't know what this specific wonder "
"does exactly, but it's fascinating to examine. It's like nothing I've ever "
"seen! I don't even recognize the materials that it's composed of, and it's "
"constantly pulsing with some kind of latent energy. What is it? Is it unique "
"or are there similar artifacts just waiting to be discovered beneath the "
"island's surface?\n"
"\n"
"My, how invigorating! Isabelle was right, this was exactly what I needed. I "
"feel like a young man again!  "
