msgctxt "Content/1225025815"
msgid ""
"Rockwell, old bean, you've done it again! Both mother and child made it "
"through, Timur is a proud father, and your head is still attached to its "
"shoulders. Why I was even a guest of honor at Timur's celebratory feast! I "
"cannot say I enjoyed the blood sport that serves as the Burning Phoenix's "
"entertainment, but the food was delectable.\n"
"\n"
"I was also sure to seize upon Timur's momentary goodwill by filling his ears "
"with whispers of obelisks, artifacts and the untold power they grant to "
"mortal men. It may take time for those thoughts to turn to action, but with "
"constant care, I may yet turn him into my unwitting general."
msgstr ""

