msgctxt "Content/2177643306"
msgid ""
"Second among his lieutenants is the white giant of wind and rime, the Lord of "
"Winter. It rules over the land of snow, but its breath is more frigid than "
"any of the storms that howl across its domain. All who feel it turn to ice, "
"frozen and unmoving.\n"
"\n"
"A feral creature, it's more ravenous than the others. More beastlike. It's "
"happy to tear and shred with fangs and claws, or impale its prey on spears of "
"ice. To stalk, to kill...this desire consumes it, and it will follow that "
"creed until there is no prey left to devour.\n"
"\n"
"Find its lair, turn the hunt upon the hunter and let the long winter thaw."
msgstr ""

