msgctxt "Content/3595535805"
msgid ""
"Simulation 157B was another failure. Error 612-A4, same as always. Almost no "
"change in reactor coupling.\n"
"\n"
"I've had projects fail, but not like this. Not this spectacularly, just "
"inches from the finish line. Why'd it have to be this one? This is the pièce "
"de résistance on my lifelong resume, it's the thing that will wipe my whole "
"ledger clean. It needs to work, or my legacy is this dead hunk of rock "
"orbiting around the sun.\n"
"\n"
"Thirty more simulations. I can get thirty more simulations in before I'll "
"need to sleep. If I can just get a different error code, then I can start to "
"isolate the variables involved. Just give me something to go on here, "
"anything at all."
