msgctxt "Content/2630034982"
msgid ""
"Step by step, I am learning how to shoot. During my first few lessons, the "
"weapons almost jumped out of my hand when I fired them, but my arms have "
"grown stronger and my aim truer.\n"
"\n"
"Captain Dahkeya's presence has been helpful. The same calm that I found "
"unnerving from afar has been steadying from up close. He does not waste his "
"breath on exaggerated praise or criticism. He simply keeps me focused on what "
"I need to do, and everything else just falls away.\n"
"\n"
"Considering where I started, he has been very patient with me. Perhaps I "
"should be more patient with him."
msgstr ""

