msgctxt "Content/1821553446"
msgid ""
"Survivors and Creatures gain experience points throughout gameplay. As you "
"gain experience, you level up and gain stat points, which can be spent to "
"improve your survival skills. Points can be allocated in; Health, Stamina, "
"Oxygen, Food, Water, Weight, Melee Damage, Movement Speed, Fortitude, and "
"Crafting Speed."
msgstr ""

