"they complete it or when time runs out."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "Content/1766083052"
msgid ""
"Survivors, creatures, and most structures have inventories. At the top of the "
"inventory, you will see two tabs. One tab is for your item storage, and the "
"other tab is for crafting new items. Below the two tabs, there is a search "
"bar for you to filter your tabs, as well as some buttons which will help you "
"manage your inventory. At the bottom of the inventory, you will see your "
"Quick Item Slots. You can place items in here to make them quickly "
"accessible. Your inventory also displays your currently equipped items which "
"you will see visible in the center."
msgstr ""

