msgctxt "Content/1990579149"
msgid ""
"Systems online and engines purring. My MEK is go for launch, so whatever did "
"this better watch its ass. Payback's coming.\n"
"\n"
"I'm competent enough with TEK armor and a rifle, but if you really want to "
"see me make magic happen, put me inside a cockpit. I might specialize in "
"fighters, but I've aced all the simulations with just about every vehicle in "
"the URE arsenal. It doesn't matter if it's got wheels, wings or legs, with a "
"machine like this at my fingertips, there's no such thing as "
"impossible.\n"
"\n"
"All right, mystery voice, keep that target locked for me. Reinforcements are "
"en route, and you'd better believe we're bringing the thunder."
msgstr ""

