msgctxt "Content/2819301116"
msgid ""
"The FSBMMs returned, and I was right - I didn't have the firepower to fight "
"them. Luckily someone else did.\n"
"It was incredible! I've never seen a human move that fast. One second, I'm a "
"dead woman, and the next there's someone in glowing, silver armor tearing "
"through those creatures like they were dodos. One got punched so hard it "
"skipped off the cavern floor!\n"
"As if a superhuman savior wasn't shocking enough, when they lifted their "
"visor, I found a familiar face. It was Mei-Yin! It took me a good minute to "
"form a sentence after that. I must have looked like a complete dipstick, "
"because I swear, she almost laughed.\n"
"At least I'm a living dipstick, and with her around, I just might stay that "
"way."
msgstr ""

