msgctxt "Content/1833378714"
msgid ""
"This Nerva bloke's FIGJAM incarnate. He seems to think that he's Jupiter's "
"gift to the Island or some rubbish like that. I think his ego was actually "
"tangible when the Legion returned from to the obelisk with the third key and "
"the head of a dragon in tow.\n"
"\n"
"Sadly, as much as I would enjoy seeing him fall flat on his face, I need him "
"and I need the New Legion. So, when he \"asked\" me to guide his forces to "
"the hidden cave, I obliged without protest.\n"
"\n"
"What he'll do with me afterwards, I don't know."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "Content/1905604586"
msgid ""
"This Nida claims to come from a long line of caretakers who lived out their "
"lives tending their gardens in the sky.\n"
"\n"
"She says we're under attack by some kind of invading force.\n"
"\n"
"I was shown visions of creatures and lands twisted out of shape in the other "
"garden-wheel.\n"
"\n"
"I felt pathetic and weak, once I understood how far outside my own time and "
"place I truly was.\n"
"\n"
"Nida told me my trials in the netherworld that she called Genesis should have "
"prepared me for our coming fight, but I was less sure.\n"
"\n"
"Then she showed me the colossal mechanical mules the caretakers use to work "
"the land, how those can cut through solid rock with spears of light as bright "
"as the sun.\n"
"\n"
"And I saw how we may not be as powerless as I'd feared."
msgstr ""

