msgctxt "Content/2712748961"
msgid ""
"This is a place of death. The ground is scarred and barren, and there is no "
"light or movement save that of the violet fire. Even Ao Yue does not seem to "
"like it. The living should not tread here.\n"
"Why would Juzi come here? What was so important that she would risk this "
"place, and why would she not tell me? Whatever the reason, it has already "
"cost some of her teammates their lives. I found their bodies earlier today, "
"mangled and partially devoured beside the remains of their beasts. Thankfully "
"Juzi was not among them.\n"
"Great towers of crystal loom ahead, where the violet fire has frozen solid. "
"Perhaps she has found shelter there."
msgstr ""

