msgctxt "Content/1345893030"
msgid ""
"This is the smoking gun. It has to be. I simply can't be convinced that this "
"place is natural after finding an island populated entirely by carnivores. "
"\n"
"\n"
"Even if they fed off of each other – which is awfully dubious given that "
"carnivore meat is much more likely to carry harmful parasites than herbivore "
"meat – the landmass is so small and their population is so dense that they "
"could never maintain it. Yet there it is, hidden away off the northeast coast "
"of the Island. Someone would have to put them there on purpose.\n"
"\n"
"There's no way that Rockwell can deny my theory now."
msgstr ""

