msgctxt "Content/3886941160"
msgid ""
"This woman, Mei-Yin... she's not like anyone I've ever met, and not just "
"because she's from hundreds of years in the past. It's those eyes, they're "
"just so intense. It's like staring into a storm.\n"
"\n"
"She caused a real stir when we first brought her back to base with her pet "
"monster, but everyone's used to her by now. Honestly I think she trusts us "
"way less than we trust her. She only seems to speak when she's doing chores, "
"and she's always got one hand on that sword of hers.\n"
"\n"
"I guess that's what it takes to survive all alone like that, but hopefully "
"she'll learn that it's okay to let her guard down. Maybe then I can really "
"meet the person behind those eyes."
msgstr ""

