msgctxt "Content/4002962056"
msgid ""
"Three days ago, I was asked to help the villagers  obtain a clutch of dragon "
"eggs. Only then did it occur to me that they did not have many creatures at "
"their command. They relied far more on their tools. Perhaps this is why they "
"were so impressed with Ao Yue.\n"
"The hunt went well. I had to do much of the work and explain many things, but "
"the others were grateful. It also let me test the limits of my armor. By now, "
"using it is no different to me than wielding a sword, and I welcomed the "
"challenge.\n"
"After the hunt, no one treats me like a child anymore, even when their tools "
"confuse me. I suppose we all have different things that we excel at."
msgstr ""

