msgctxt "Content/2264966721"
msgid ""
"Time to go over the facts. \n"
"\n"
"Like the island, this desert is a space station posing as a natural "
"environment. It is inhabited by a large population of dangerous, genetically "
"engineered creatures, and a small population of humans that are struggling to "
"survive. This whole environment is then deliberately contained by a "
"combination of a holographic horizon and natural barriers.\n"
"\n"
"Assuming the other space stations are at all similar, then this whole thing "
"is starting to look like some kind of bizarre experiment on a grand scale. "
