msgctxt "Content/1720536926"
msgid ""
"Training grew easier once my charges began to see the results. In fact, "
"they've found such a wellspring of enthusiasm that their drills and chores "
"alone cannot contain it. This morning, I found a flag flying above the "
"armory. It was the symbol of the Imperial Legion, but with one of the "
"island's flying lizards replacing the eagle and words in a foreign language "
"replacing SPQR. I’m told they say \"The New Legion.\" I admit, I smiled at "
"the sight.\n"
"\n"
"Very well then. It's time to find out if I've created true Legionnaires. We "
"march at dawn.\n"
"\n"
"Gaius Marcellus Nerva\n"
