"Trent, my friend, your sacrifice was not in vain. At long last, I have found "
"the third artifact we sought. It took many failed expeditions, but to get "
"lost is to learn the way. For every wrong turn, I mapped out a new part of "
"these caverns, and now I know them as well as I know myself.\n"
"\n"
"I will gather my creatures and head for the terminal in the morning. If "
"Boris' notes were right, these artifacts should be able to activate it. I'm "
"not sure what will happen after that, but it can't be worse than the fate "
"that awaits me here.\n"
"\n"
"If only the others were alive to see this day. If only I'd been able to save "
"them too..."
msgstr ""

