msgctxt "Content/1509847522"
msgid ""
"Turns out no one else had a better plan, so the wheels are in motion. I've "
"already got teams working on the hangars and gathering resources while I "
"hammer out the schematics.\n"
"\n"
"Building these MEKs is going to be one of the hardest things I've ever done, "
"maybe the hardest. With the Gateway Project, I could use the Obelisks as a "
"blueprint, but these are all me. Luckily, having an eidetic memory means I "
"can call on everything I ever studied about robotics, so I'm not starting "
"from scratch.\n"
"\n"
"Besides, this is my true Iove. They say constantly crunching away on a big "
"project will make anyone burn out, but for me it feels like a dip in a "
"lazarus pit. I live for the grind. "
msgstr ""

