msgctxt "Content/145448941"
msgid ""
"Xenobiology isn't really my thing-I generally do biochemical work at the "
"micro level.\n"
"\n"
"I know how to run samples of the invasive flora and fauna from the "
"contaminated ring through our array of analytical equipment, but when it "
"comes to interpreting the results I'm mostly at a loss.\n"
"\n"
"Anyone could see that these invaders are wildly exotic and demonstrably "
"hostile, but beyond that, I'd just be guessing at what I'm looking "
"at.\n"
"\n"
"That said, I'm relatively sure that a lot of what I sampled were genetically-"
"modified organisms-like our maewings-possibly created using commandeered "
"equipment in the other ring.\n"
"\n"
"Unlike maewings, all of these organisms seem to have been created to "
"establish an aggressive perimeter defense.\n"
"\n"
"Defense of what, I'm not exactly sure...\n"
"\n"
"I'm back to suspecting our Homo deus visitor is responsible, but I haven't "
"even mentioned the most damning evidence-I think I'm seeing traces of Element "
"in these samples, the same alien material that poisoned our home "
"planet.\n"
"\n"
"Element, incorporated into living, mutated tissue.\n"
"If I'm right, this is extremely bad news."
msgstr ""

