msgctxt "Content/1547940792"
msgid ""
"You know, this whole \"staving off the ever looming spectre of despair\" "
"thing would be a lot easier without all the dinosaurs. Did I not mention "
"those? I should have mentioned those. Anyway, turns out that raptor attacks "
"aren't so great for morale. True story.\n"
"\n"
"At least the weather's holding up. We've had clear skies for three days now. "
"It was a good idea to start giving people callsigns, too. Getting a new "
"callsign from my squadron always made me feel closer to them, whatever it "
"was. Hopefully it works with this bunch.\n"
"\n"
"The newbie suggested Rubberneck for me, since I keep looking at the sky, but "
"I can't help it. It really is gorgeous here. A perfect blue."
msgstr ""

