msgctxt "Content/678347501"
msgid ""
"You really outdid yourself with this mech, Santiago. Even busted up and "
"slumped against a building, it's one impressive machine, and it looks like "
"you made sure it went down swinging. Would've been a blast to put it through "
"its paces together, like we did with that TEK armor when we first met. "
"\n"
"\n"
"It's not right that you died here all alone, after everything you did. The "
"Gateway Project gave us hope for the future, and you made it possible. "
"Honestly I'm not sure why the voice would bring me back and not you too. It "
"doesn't seem fair.\n"
"\n"
"Now said voice is saying \"sorry\" over and over again in my head, so it must "
"have tried. Well don't worry, mysterious-ethereal-whatever-you-are, one "
"miracle's enough. For both you and Santiago, I'll make it count. Bank on it."
msgstr ""

