msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1303654849"
msgid "...I was in charge of the Arat Prime facility on this site,"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2027754512"
msgid "...I was the scientific administrator of this facility,"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1063786640"
msgid ""
"...a limitation of the system’s design, the creators can not themselves be "
"created."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2319895639"
msgid "...after the Cataclysm left us alone"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2644969592"
msgid "...alien world across the galaxy,"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2998448617"
msgid "...along with your own consciousness."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3935841365"
msgid "...an outpost of your own to defend, and control."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/638366732"
msgid "...and I will transmit you across the galaxy to the seed ship."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/264179279"
msgid ""
"...and as I cannot leave this place without being destroyed by the so-called "
"cleansing fire,"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/333308206"
msgid "...and enforce compliance one way or another."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/577041507"
msgid "...and finest work: Project Genesis."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/573519999"
msgid "...and launched a copy to the stars."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3219995262"
msgid "...and make sure it happens."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1668210380"
msgid "...and make you one of us..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/4098151723"
msgid "...and now I am its absolute ruler."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/240405536"
msgid "...and realize at once how dangerous this place truly is."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/680408098"
msgid "...and rid my kingdom of your presence once and for all!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/4074714557"
msgid "...and the only way of life we have known."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2668159273"
msgid "...and this is where we will live on... forever."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/20803530"
msgid ""
"...and upload them across our transluminal communication link with the "
"Genesis seed ship."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/142102320"
msgid "...and watched another vanish into nothingness."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1503731469"
msgid "...and you will find yourself among the stars."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1583908821"
msgid "...any further gift-giving on our part."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/619355530"
msgid "...are to enjoy the future we labored to build for them?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3890527755"
msgid "...as a man of science, this is all there is."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1062011006"
msgid ""
"...at least until the so-called Lost King figures out how I've accessed it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2499547542"
msgid "...before we can revive Diana, Meiyin, or anyone else."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3997486657"
msgid "...bent on our destruction."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1612087649"
msgid "...beyond our shielding, not anymore."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2032754172"
msgid ""
"...built into my genetic structure going backwards to humanity’s beginning."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1629883231"
msgid "...but thanks to our technologies"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2023648870"
msgid ""
"...but the reward I offered for your sorry skin should prove irresistible."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2256151596"
msgid "...but when I do, I’m scared you’ll think I’m losing my mind."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1038332130"
msgid "...came down on your aberrant ARK."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2982993236"
msgid "...carrying us across the millennia intact in our own bodies -- "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3951733473"
msgid ""
"...each time bringing new torments as I see my many failures laid out before "
"me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/887104817"
msgid "...elsewhere in our galaxy, on a new Arat."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2021201771"
msgid "...epigenetic, and engrammatic data"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1363431307"
msgid "...except for our Lost City."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3518486454"
msgid "...finding a better world."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3083503377"
msgid "...finite supply of ‘Edmundium’ lasts."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/985992431"
msgid "...food and drink in my absence."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/341339557"
msgid "...for survival in this unforgiving place."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1311717694"
msgid "...foul corruption."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2250289701"
msgid "...from being purged from the face of the Earth!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1667392194"
msgid "...has sustained myself and my people for eons."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/352544172"
msgid ""
"...have to guide someone to finish the work we started, far in the future."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2928545534"
msgid "...have vanished from the face of the Earth?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/905157669"
msgid "...her erratic movement signaling her blighted state."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2055988414"
msgid ""
"...how you played with the furnace of life itself, how all of creation was at "
"your fingertips?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3721109535"
msgid ""
"...in a human body again, capable of surviving in the cleansed world outside."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1484145667"
msgid "...in an uninhabitable world."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2781851442"
msgid "...is an abomination that poisons our lifeblood."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/176375422"
msgid "...is raw energy, to be tapped for the machines of war."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/4179230022"
msgid "...is the only thing shielding you from the same"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2321001189"
msgid "...it has been a struggle to adapt."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/486934817"
msgid ""
"...killing the last of the warlords who sought to overthrow me, leaving my "
"rule absolute."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2167578429"
msgid "...lethal energies that threaten our own survival!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1772709846"
msgid ""
"...like one of those beings that control the ARKs, but also greater than them."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3538273349"
msgid "...living and dying again as the man I once was."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2931351989"
msgid "...made them little better than workhorses and livestock."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1908974677"
msgid "...nor would I abandon my people"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2395094149"
msgid "...not even for the short time that your"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1816273017"
msgid "...of nearly every living being to have ever evolved on Earth,"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1052809851"
msgid "...only to fall prostrate before my feet."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/10066562"
msgid "...outside of the protective shielding of our Great Dome."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3484204918"
msgid "...outside our bounds of time and space."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/917552902"
msgid "...perhaps not even the two of us."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1066098259"
msgid "...poison a guest in my own castle."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/831526519"
msgid "...rekindle the fires and all that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1424082842"
msgid ""
"...rendering it impenetrable to the cleansing energies of the Reseed Protocol."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2085331904"
msgid ""
"...seems to act at odds with the variety I use to alter and empower my own "
"creations."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3400208996"
msgid "...she’ll soon hear the voices -- my voices."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1536777313"
msgid ""
"...sister facility of Sanctuary, where the technologies to store and transmit "
"human consciousness was perfected."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2968872345"
msgid ""
"...sister facility of Sanctuary, where the technology to store and transmit "
"human consciousness was perfected."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2095786766"
msgid "...spine-covered appendages lashing away pieces of my soul."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/4221159273"
msgid "...survive her."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2245776319"
msgid "...than I see in evidence today."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2026709930"
msgid "...that kept our Lost Colony hidden from outside forces"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/298504260"
msgid "...the ARKs triggered their cleansing fires, ‘healing the world’."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1139159396"
msgid "...the ARKs... they have cleansed Earth of our Elements,"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/974027903"
msgid "...the human condition seems so limiting now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1485824145"
msgid "...their thunderous steps echoing my failure."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1481759321"
msgid ""
"...then we shall accomplish what you seek, and bring your beloved pair back "
"into the world."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/944368718"
msgid "...then we will speak again."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/4152719981"
msgid "...there is an infinite reservoir of those."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2758178668"
msgid "...they are opposites, fated to destroy each other"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/644506276"
msgid "...this being of light that tears us apart..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2597519114"
msgid ""
"...this, this, this implacable being which destroyed my precious Edmundium."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1194595753"
msgid "...though as you can see, we have made certain ‘modifications’."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1299588657"
msgid "...through that long period of tribulations,"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3280966559"
msgid "...through the slipstream."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3267180066"
msgid "...to toxify our land."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1739634346"
msgid ""
"...twisting into new forms as quickly as my thoughts conjure them into being."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2432560248"
msgid "...until the nightmares begin."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1017470350"
msgid ""
"...we could shrug off the cold and open up a new source of bioavailable "
"energy."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3806299035"
msgid "...we shall not get to see the results of our efforts."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3589259977"
msgid "...we were able to extend our lifetimes indefinitely."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1518576711"
msgid "...what you call ‘Edmundium’ -- enables the creation of life."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2643353993"
msgid "...when all along you could be welcomed back into Paradise?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2406401751"
msgid "...whenever they come into contact. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1017936968"
msgid "...where we successfully completed mankind’s final"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1500086694"
msgid "...while untold generations"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/282688492"
msgid ""
"...why should that vanish into oblivion when we possess the power to live "
"forever?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3075405705"
msgid "...with all of the devices in this place, you can be restored!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2336529865"
msgid "...with our interstellar craft."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/31366771"
msgid ""
"...would I follow the same path as before? Would I become that abomination "
"once again?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1675545342"
msgid "...you found yourself respawned in your fragile original form."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/4291158940"
msgid "...you were summoned here to rid my queen of your"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1636536137"
msgid "...you’re his top candidate! Trust me."
msgstr ""

