msgid ""
"<<Lost King Darius I and Edmund Rockwell>> Archival Audio 001\n"
"Cross-Reference: <<Edmund Rockwell>>\n"
"\n"
"The following conversation took place in the Great Hall of the Royal Palace "
"atop Arat Prime, as the Lost King granted an audience to Rockwell."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3938376686"
msgid ""
"<<Lost King Darius I and Edmund Rockwell>> Archival Audio 002\n"
"Cross-Reference:  <<Lost Queen>>\n"
"\n"
"The following conversation took place in the Reception Chamber of the Royal "
"Palace atop Arat Prime, as the Lost King returned to confront Rockwell after "
"tending to the stricken Lost Queen."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3336830531"
msgid ""
"<<Lost King Darius I and Edmund Rockwell>> Archival Audio 003\n"
"Cross-Reference:  <<Lost Queen>>\n"
"\n"
"The following conversation took place in the Reception Chamber of the Royal "
"Palace atop Arat Prime, where Rockwell had been left under guard while the "
"Lost King was again at the Lost Queen's side."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1282118652"
msgid ""
"<<Lost King Darius I and Edmund Rockwell>> Archival Audio 004\n"
"Cross-Reference:  <<Lost Queen>>\n"
"\n"
"The following conversation took place in the Reception Chamber of the Royal "
"Palace atop Arat Prime, after Rockwell had been devising a cure for the Lost "
"Queen's contamination."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1192076116"
msgid ""
"<<Lost King Darius I and Edmund Rockwell>> Archival Audio 005\n"
"Cross-Reference: <<Genesis Seed Ship>>\n"
"\n"
"The following conversation took place in the Reception Chamber, and the "
"Throne Room's Codex Chamber, of the Royal Palace atop Arat Prime, just after "
"Rockwell cured the Lost Queen's poisoning using a chelating agent of his own "
"design."
msgstr ""

