msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/326932360"
msgid ""
"A community classic ARK map returns, updated for the Official Server "
"networks! Crystal Isles is 150 square kilometers of awe-inspiring biomes… "
"Build bases high in forest canopy and floating islands, and tame your own "
"Tropeognathus to ride into aerial combat!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/22664315"
msgid ""
"A desperate voice calls out to you from across the galaxy... long ago you "
"helped her restored life to the extinct Earth, and now she needs your skills "
"once more. She seeks the engram Codex, hidden in a lost kingdom at the end of "
"the world: Arat Prime. Discover the dark secrets of this forlorn place as you "
"master arcane skills, tame strange cryptofauna, cloaking yourself in powerful "
"accursed gear. Survive its challenges & assemble an army of Thralls, as you "
"seek to dethrone the Lost King and change the fate of the future!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2784110768"
msgid ""
"A desperate voice calls to you from across the galaxy... You once helped her "
"restore life to the extinct Earth, and now she needs your help again. She "
"seeks the engram Codex, hidden in a lost kingdom at the end of the world. "
"Discover the dark secrets of this forlorn place as you master arcane skills, "
"tame strange cryptofauna, and cloak yourself in the accursed gear of the "
"inhabitants. Survive long enough, and you may even gather an army of Thralls "
"as you seek to dethrone the Lost King!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/149315438"
msgid ""
"A highly competitive tournament version of Poker.\n"
"Players sit down and wager any Items they want in a long-form tournament-"
"style game. All players must agree to wagered Items before the game begins. "
"Blinds increase as the game goes on, and play continues until one player wins "
"all the chips. The winning player keeps all the wagered Items."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3538061898"
msgid "A life lived on a world long since dead, as a once-heralded scientist."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/130291518"
msgid ""
"A more casual version of Poker where players may come and go.\n"
"Players may only buy-in with the table's pre-selected Item type. Each copy of "
"that Item \"purchases\" chips from the table, which can be used to play. "
"Blinds never increase, and players may come and go as they wish. When a "
"player leaves the table, they exchange their chips for the table's pre-"
"determined Item."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1591752194"
msgid ""
"A novel red isotope of the exotic Element powering our civilization has been "
"discovered inside our borders, deep under the Antarctic ice."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2467712437"
msgid ""
"A person could close their eyes here and then awake to open their eyes on an "
"alien world in the distant future, with no sense of lost continuity."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1550089033"
msgid "A pity I could not examine her more closely to be sure."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/244094896"
msgid ""
"A renewed vigor courses through me. A will to survive. And more than that... "
"to perpetuate."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3548013255"
