msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3323572728"
msgid "Bob's Tall Tale"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/914863260"
msgid "Bob's Tall Tales"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/4276701030"
msgid ""
"Bob:  (groan) Before we keep going, I was thinking maybe you wanna let your "
"dad know where you ran off to?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/739137105"
msgid ""
"Bob:  (groan)... You just sit tight while your Unka Bob thinks about how to "
"tell the next part without giving nightmares."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1503196133"
msgid ""
"Bob:  (gulp) Yeah, well, your old man’s gonna come looking for me, he finds "
"out I gave you bad dreams."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/4222831706"
msgid "Bob:  (sigh)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/467244632"
msgid "Bob:  ...I’d found a place worth building up into something."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/4164041452"
msgid ""
"Bob:  ...and you'll always need to stick by the folks who have your back."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3169615996"
msgid "Bob:  ...but that’s what worked for me back on The Island."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/165880501"
msgid "Bob:  ...like we were on the world’s biggest ‘Tilt-A-Whirl’!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/457784444"
msgid "Bob:  ...something in the sky."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3648962111"
msgid "Bob:  ...until I spotted a cave that looked like the Promised Land."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3136412820"
msgid ""
"Bob:  A couple of his compadres tried to take revenge. Wasn’t much of a fair "
"fight."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/4199719000"
msgid "Bob:  A lot worse."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2424706615"
msgid "Bob:  About why the big man... thinks the way he does."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3301482221"
msgid ""
"Bob:  Actually... your dad. Well, he paid the big price to save everyone."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2628921729"
msgid ""
"Bob:  After I had my fill of drinking from bug behinds, I decided to try for "
"one of the camel-lizards I saw waddling around that sandpit."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1168101736"
msgid ""
"Bob:  After I stopped the bugs from ransacking that whistlestop, I guess I "
"thought maybe..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2414510689"
msgid ""
"Bob:  After all we’d gone through to get back to Earth, it was a real kick in "
"the gut to see how dead the place was."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1886615609"
msgid ""
"Bob:  After scavenging a while, we found a fountain that was still working "
"somehow."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/188534300"
msgid ""
"Bob:  After seeing them ruins up close for myself, we decided it probably was "
"time for us to mosey along."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2488888732"
msgid "Bob:  Ah, THERE you are! Was wondering where you two got off to."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1968676041"
msgid ""
"Bob:  All right then. Let’s start at the very beginning, on a faraway "
"tropical island, surrounded by sparkling blue water."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/255987767"
msgid ""
"Bob:  Almost like they’d known each other before. Probably more of that "
"‘future’ gobbledygoop that gives me a headache."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3983375704"
msgid "Bob:  Along with Helena, Mei-Yin, and -- surprise, surprise -- Diana."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/558108226"
msgid "Bob:  Along with Mei-Yin, and -- surprise, surprise -- Diana."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1121570100"
msgid "Bob:  Am I telling this story, or are you?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3710096750"
msgid ""
"Bob:  And I said maybe we should name the park around it for her pilot friend."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/803451709"
msgid ""
"Bob:  And I, uh -- well, there’s no good way to say this -- I took a drink "
"from it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1025544530"
msgid "Bob:  And I’m sure she wasn’t happy getting stuck with me, either."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/326758900"
msgid ""
"Bob:  And cooked everything topside. The whole surface of the ARK went up in "
"flames."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3258381"
msgid ""
"Bob:  And it ain’t easy trying to survive out there all by your lonesome."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3250602056"
msgid ""
"Bob:  And it turned out Santiago was one of the people best suited to fight "
"inside of those things..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3158061692"
msgid "Bob:  And it was the first place I ran into her..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1530568634"
msgid ""
"Bob:  And she tells me, “Bob, you’re the greatest guy ever! You have to stay "
"alive, so you can save everyone!\""
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3555351661"
msgid ""
"Bob:  And so with the band all back together again at the very end, how could "
"we lose?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1161012909"
msgid "Bob:  And that’s when Momma -- an honest-to-gosh dragon -- turned up."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1083500800"
msgid "Bob:  And then we put that twisted freak out of his misery... and ours."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/59738169"
msgid "Bob:  And they didn’t much appreciate us."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3039370591"
msgid "Bob:  And... people were stored there, too."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3669236165"
msgid "Bob:  Anyhow, THOSE are the kinds of tough calls a chief’s gotta make."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3931637495"
msgid "Bob:  Anyway, whatever you wanna call it, it caused a real ruckus."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2166662602"
msgid ""
"Bob:  Anyway, yeah -- it was too hot to run around like that. And I burnt "
"myself out quick."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2354957822"
msgid "Bob:  Anyway, you’ll never guess who was in charge of their outfit."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3843963562"
msgid ""
"Bob:  Anyways, I guess I finally hit one on its noggin enough times for it to "
"think we were pals."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1759393504"
msgid ""
"Bob:  Anyways, before I could round up those two eggheads, the whole place "
"started spinning and shaking itself to pieces..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3235348313"
msgid ""
"Bob:  Around that time, your old man took me with him on a scouting mission "
"into the city ruins."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/513316244"
msgid ""
"Bob:  At first, things were more weird than scary down there, like something "
"out of the funny pages."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1674957479"
msgid ""
"Bob:  At that point, not much else left to do -- ‘cept dig in and try to "
"start over. But at least we wouldn’t have to do that from scratch."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1291607196"
msgid "Bob:  Atta girl. ‘Cause this next bit, well..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3341713320"
msgid ""
"Bob:  Aussies with their funny accents -- and don’t even get me started on "
"those Kiwis, sheesh..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/981550311"
msgid ""
"Bob:  Aw, kid... I didn’t know your mom, but your dad -- I mean, I’m sure he "
"knows what she’d have wanted."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1157656235"
msgid ""
"Bob:  Aw... wouldn’t you rather hear that story from the big guy himself?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2674260942"
msgid ""
"Bob:  BUT... your dad’s been trying to protect you until we figure out what "
"the heck’s going on here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/685434472"
msgid "Bob:  Be glad you get to be picky, kid. That means you’re well fed."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3470254550"
msgid ""
"Bob:  Been thinkin’ maybe we’re all here on this new world today for some "
"reason like that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2117303239"
msgid ""
"Bob:  Believe you me, spoke for all of us when he said he wanted to forget "
"all about the place..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2294938389"
msgid "Bob:  Big Bug Bandit reached for his pistol, but I had the quicker draw."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/750004312"
msgid ""
"Bob:  But I must've been knocked upside the head during our tussle, 'cause I "
"don't remember the next part so good."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1144990383"
msgid ""
"Bob:  But all our thoughts of long, easy lives went away real quick when we "
"got our first look at ol’ King Titan."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1154032586"
msgid ""
"Bob:  But before I could come up with a plan to save us, this crazy desert "
"witch showed up with... a dragon!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1546825345"
msgid ""
"Bob:  But before Santiago took us topside, we had to suit ourselves up in "
"that shiny future-armor of theirs."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3851837135"
msgid ""
"Bob:  But maybe that’s a story for another time. I mean you got to have some "
"chores to get back to--"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/4292376455"
msgid ""
"Bob:  But whatever the danger, Bob still managed to show the wild ‘n’ wooly "
"wastelands who was boss."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1564678590"
msgid "Bob:  Careful what you wish for. Things got weird and dark down there..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3267424469"
msgid ""
"Bob:  Clones. Copies of our original selves, but with our memories and, I "
"dunno, maybe our souls too."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2095528722"
msgid "Bob:  Darlin’, you don’t know the half of it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/157098053"
msgid "Bob:  Didn’t much like the sound of that. I never did tan that well."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1775501670"
msgid ""
"Bob:  Doc Rockwell in particular kept wandering deeper and deeper in, where I "
"couldn’t keep an eye on him."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/660781878"
msgid "Bob:  Don’t think Diana trusted ol’ Doc Rockwell."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3789753106"
msgid ""
"Bob:  Errr, no... I mean, the future to me. But what do I know, I’m just some "
"grunt who bought the big one in 1944."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/160698528"
msgid "Bob:  Especially for poor Doc Rockwell."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3427144518"
msgid ""
"Bob:  Even armored up, we had to wait until things cooled down after dark "
"before we could follow your dad outside."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3795032426"
msgid "Bob:  Everyone?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/573863496"
msgid "Bob:  Family’s gotta stick together."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1504519051"
msgid ""
"Bob:  Figure of speech, darlin’. Means we were about to have us a good, old-"
"fashioned shootout!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/686419629"
msgid "Bob:  Fine by me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1014037949"
msgid ""
"Bob:  Fine. You just sit tight, while your Unka Bob thinks about how to tell "
"the next part without giving nightmares..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2462247391"
msgid ""
"Bob:  For a guy who keeps ending up in charge of people, I swear Santiago was "
"always happiest with a welding torch in his hands."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/523754374"
msgid ""
"Bob:  From up there, we could make out broken domes across the wasteland -- "
"with floating towers just like the ones on the ARKs."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1355660833"
msgid ""
"Bob:  Funny thing: all that shaking left a buncha stuff lying around that I "
"could see was gonna come in handy."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1963722507"
msgid ""
"Bob:  Gave us a whole shopping list of stuff to find for him. Said he wanted "
"to build a faster way to get around."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2422493423"
msgid "Bob:  Go ask Santiago yourself, if you don’t believe me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2452890472"
msgid "Bob:  Good instincts, hers."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2226128547"
msgid ""
"Bob:  Great. Guess I’ll just, uh -- keep retelling these true tales about "
"Bob’s amazing adventures..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1486033829"
msgid "Bob:  Had enough responsibility in the army back in my day."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2996693214"
msgid "Bob:  Had me going in circles, trying like heck to find a place to hide."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/650883720"
msgid ""
"Bob:  He used it to change himself into something straight out of a creature-"
"feature."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1282648387"
msgid ""
"Bob:  He wanted time to come up with a new secret weapon -- something big "
"enough to go toe-to-toe with that Titan."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/4171975751"
msgid ""
"Bob:  He was too busy gawking at all the shiny toys those Future-People had "
"brought to the camp."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/669123773"
msgid "Bob:  He wouldn’t listen to anyone that tried to warn him, neither."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1503214865"
msgid ""
"Bob:  Hey now -- the Doc wanted to bring someone back with that stuff. Didn’t "
"work out so good for him, did it?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3199827534"
msgid "Bob:  Hey now, I was talking about it giving ME nightmares."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2668795658"
msgid "Bob:  Hey now, I was talking about it giving me nightmares"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1252089108"
msgid "Bob:  Hey, that’s not bad! And this is you over here, with this dumdum?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2218741562"
msgid ""
"Bob:  He’d been acting extra squirrelly by then, and she seemed worried he’d "
"gone completely off his nut."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3563011291"
msgid "Bob:  He’s your dad, Meeka."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2599608620"
msgid "Bob:  How about we call this one..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3023463480"
msgid ""
"Bob:  How many times had we died and been brought back already? Just thinking "
"about it gave me the heebie-jeebies."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3787035765"
msgid ""
"Bob:  Huh. Yeah. That’s where ol’ Santiago and I met for the very first time!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2865872752"
msgid "Bob:  Huh? Oh. Oh wow!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3702307997"
msgid ""
"Bob:  I could see the gears turning in Santiago’s head before he finally "
"spoke up."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3472924234"
msgid ""
"Bob:  I couldn’t exactly say no... not in front of the ladies. Gotta keep up "
"my reputation, and all."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/908872114"
msgid "Bob:  I did have a little help."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/796674273"
msgid ""
"Bob:  I didn’t have much of a choice, so I let the Witch pin a star on me and "
"set me up with a trusty six-shooter."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3749503911"
msgid "Bob:  I don’t know the half of what actually went on down there."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2720911554"
msgid ""
"Bob:  I got paired up with the Beast Queen, who wasn’t much fun to be around "
"after we lost Diana."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/45318722"
msgid ""
"Bob:  I hadn’t been there since WW2. We were seeing what was left after the "
"final war."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/325643204"
msgid "Bob:  I introduced him to my pals... not that Doc even noticed. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2333951870"
msgid ""
"Bob:  I just nodded along and smiled, even though I knew we were all done-for."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/586923205"
msgid ""
"Bob:  I knew I was a goner, unless I could scrounge up something to drink, "
"and pronto..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3941246054"
msgid "Bob:  I like to think we made it sorry for messing with us."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/4080291486"
msgid ""
"Bob:  I pointed out the flowers by the fountain, and told him the Beast "
"Queen, Mei-Yin, had been leaving ‘em in memory of Diana."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1300662550"
msgid "Bob:  I think -- well, I better not tell you MY crackpot ideas."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3750656334"
msgid "Bob:  I told ‘em, “Thanks, but no thanks.”"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2622373807"
msgid ""
"Bob:  I tripped over a bunch of eggs lying around inside, and thought I’d hit "
"the jackpot."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/454469635"
msgid ""
"Bob:  If you could call that living. Poor critters were all messed up from "
"the poisons out in the wastes... "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3020650664"
msgid ""
"Bob:  In fact, you’d be surprised what you’re willing to eat when you’re "
"starving for real."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1326695081"
msgid ""
"Bob:  Inside was enough of that Tek stuff to make your dad grin like he’d hit "
"the jackpot. We crammed all we could fit into the trunk."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2381481637"
msgid "Bob:  It was game-on."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3509099802"
msgid ""
"Bob:  It was him, all right. And he said we were all gonna be okay, as long "
"as those Tek supplies keep crashing to Earth."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1619333724"
msgid "Bob:  It’s filled with some tough memories for ol’ Bob."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1470220419"
msgid ""
"Bob:  Just goes to show -- you gotta stay ready for the unexpected, and "
"always need to stick by the folks who have your back."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3221851775"
msgid "Bob:  Just goes to show -- you gotta stay ready for the unexpected..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/363301467"
msgid ""
"Bob:  Listen, I get that you’re mad at him now, but Santiago was there for "
"your Unka Bob when it counted."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2708984379"
msgid ""
"Bob:  Little Miss Professor and the Doc couldn’t get enough of it all. Sheesh."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/4201271185"
msgid "Bob:  Little Miss Professor here... and the Doc."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/509016839"
msgid ""
"Bob:  Little Miss Professor was making a big deal about her still being alive."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1067515423"
msgid ""
"Bob:  Look, kid... being chief’s all about making hard choices. I know I’d "
"never want that job."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1700888040"
msgid ""
"Bob:  Lucky it was him behind the wheel though, ‘cause one of those supply "
"drops came crashing down smack right in front of us!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/190898507"
msgid "Bob:  Made that jug-bug jump a mile, not that I blame it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3780230035"
msgid ""
"Bob:  Maybe it’s a good thing, you drawing all the crazy mischief I got up to "
"in the old days."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/115547807"
msgid "Bob:  Messed around with some mumbo jumbo he shouldn’t have."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/190846452"
msgid ""
"Bob:  Might help me remember things better next time some kid starts hanging "
"around me like a bad smell..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3496981189"
msgid "Bob:  Mmm... just like chicken."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3937739048"
msgid ""
"Bob:  Naturally everyone turned to me first, but I nipped that idea in the "
"bud real quick."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1732457682"
msgid ""
"Bob:  No one else seemed to want it, either. Maybe that’s why we held the "
"vote while your dad was -- uh, chopping logs."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1610555006"
msgid ""
"Bob:  No time to worry over how I ended up there or why. All I knew was I had "
"to run for cover."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3172496610"
msgid ""
"Bob:  None of ‘em so much as got a bead on me before I’d dropped all four of "
"'em in the dust with their pal."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2580669208"
msgid ""
"Bob:  Not a fan myself, but Doc Rockwell said, “Gonna need to adapt to "
"survive”."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2772277810"
msgid ""
"Bob:  Not so sure about that. His people had to rush underground after your "
"dad messed-up on the first try..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3158152046"
msgid "Bob:  Not sure why I ever listened to that old kook."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3882885799"
msgid ""
"Bob:  Now I may not know a lot, and I made plenty of my own mistakes back in "
"my day, but I do know one thing."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2181789325"
msgid ""
"Bob:  Now that I had the whole gang’s attention, I backed up a few paces and "
"told the gangleader to slap leather."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2672333666"
msgid ""
"Bob:  Now that I was the law in that forsaken outpost, I could see I was "
"gonna have to do a bit of pest control."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1721536604"
msgid ""
"Bob:  Now that we had set up a base camp, our little tribe of misfits "
"realized we were gonna need a chief."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1321368452"
msgid ""
"Bob:  Now, before you judge me on this next part, you got to understand it "
"was a life-or-death situation."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3736022962"
msgid "Bob:  Now, where was I? Oh, oh yeah--"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1776813442"
msgid ""
"Bob:  Of course, yeah. But now I had someone else to look after, which can be "
"-- you know... exhausting."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1988795332"
msgid "Bob:  Oh yeah. Uh, sorry. Anyhow, that story can wait..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3952969970"
msgid ""
"Bob:  Oh yeah? Lessee, I told you about Little Miss Professor Helena, and the "
"Beast Queen."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/743495435"
msgid "Bob:  Oh, now look kid -- I didn’t mean that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/822547702"
msgid ""
"Bob:  Okay! Okay... How ‘bout a story with spurs and six shooters, and all "
"that?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1586105187"
msgid "Bob:  Okay, okay! (sigh)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/220228552"
msgid "Bob:  Once we’d seen King Titan, we knew..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3161778041"
msgid ""
"Bob:  Once your dad was head honcho, he decided to put everyone to work "
"scrounging the ruins for scrap."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/713813822"
msgid ""
"Bob:  People weren’t ever going to be in charge of a world with monsters of "
"that size stomping around."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/805110743"
msgid "Bob:  Pestering me for my dumb tales..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/232020445"
msgid ""
"Bob:  Place was hotter’n heck, and all that danged dust had a way of workin’ "
"its way up yer, uh -- nose."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2595649711"
msgid ""
"Bob:  Point is, I was gonna have to get lean & mean if I was fixin’ to tame "
"anything in that forsaken desert!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/482139915"
msgid ""
"Bob:  Reckon I’ll spare you knowing how I figured out a way of drinking from "
"those smelly humps."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3450325500"
msgid ""
"Bob:  Right about when I’d almost given up hope, I spotted Little Miss "
"Professor again..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1045701329"
msgid ""
"Bob:  Right now, you need to find something for your pal Honker here to eat."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1405198490"
msgid ""
"Bob:  Said she and her friends had a regular boomtown going across the "
"desert, that got blown to heck by..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1140125312"
msgid ""
"Bob:  Santiago called it, uh -- ‘respawn’ Diana for one last helluva fight."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/799973141"
msgid ""
"Bob:  Santiago picked a funny place to park and run his war plan by me on our "
"way back to camp."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3042316224"
msgid ""
"Bob:  Santiago said the ARK’s ‘Tek’ was from further into the future than his "
"own time, but he still thought he could get it to work for us."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/4221039732"
msgid "Bob:  Santiago wanted another crack at it, and asked if we wanted in."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/667312190"
msgid ""
"Bob:  Say… have I ever told you the story about how your dad and I saved "
"everyone together?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2606797513"
msgid ""
"Bob:  See, the people around at the end left a lot of salvageable junk behind "
"for us. And like they say: \"One man’s trash...\""
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/4098098843"
msgid ""
"Bob:  See, this is the point in our story where things get dark… real dark."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2085936030"
msgid ""
"Bob:  She offered to fly us to see the ruins for ourselves. Not sure why I "
"let the Professor and the Doc talk me into that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1322485706"
msgid ""
"Bob:  She really took it hard, what Rockwell did to her... ‘good friend’."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3453255110"
msgid "Bob:  She was none too happy about me scrambling up her babies."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3992177868"
msgid ""
"Bob:  So I called out the biggest bug, and told him they’d best skedaddle "
"before sundown, lest I commence to stepping on ‘em."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1033905712"
msgid ""
"Bob:  So I had things MOSTLY under control before that scary dame showed me "
"up in her FANCY armor."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2608628571"
msgid ""
"Bob:  So at first, I guess, your old man was having trouble puzzling out the "
"crazy super-science running the ARKs."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1135158329"
msgid ""
"Bob:  So it was all over by the time your dad caught up with us, to say he’d "
"rigged a way for us to leave that ARK behind for Earth."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2712213419"
msgid ""
"Bob:  So that’s how I went from squeezing water from a cactus to fighting a "
"manti-whatzit in a ghost town."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1121973655"
msgid ""
"Bob:  So there I was -- whizzing through the sky -- when this sparkly lady "
"flies right up alongside me..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2178970520"
msgid ""
"Bob:  So we’d survived everything else just to wind up in a high-octane, "
"chrome-knuckled junkyard dogfight over the last scraps on Earth!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3335907961"
msgid "Bob:  So yeah, there were people from the future on that ARK."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/270582514"
msgid ""
"Bob:  So your dad ‘n’ me left the city walls and set out across the wastes, "
"to see what’d been falling out of the sky."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1287725477"
msgid ""
"Bob:  Somehow I was tumbling through the sky again, heading elsewhere in a "
"hurry..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/858344037"
msgid ""
"Bob:  Somehow she’d wound up in that dustpatch with me, which probably meant "
"that the Doc was around someplace too."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/83604240"
msgid ""
"Bob:  Someone from back on that jungle island. The ‘Beast Queen’, she called "
"herself."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/4111697220"
msgid ""
"Bob:  Someone who’d protect regular townsfolk, whether it was from rustlers, "
"bandits, or -- in this case -- bug-monsters."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/892704961"
msgid ""
"Bob:  Still, Diana decided to hang back at the camp, while the other two "
"ladies and me went along on Santiago’s crazy mission."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2471572460"
msgid ""
"Bob:  Suddenly I found myself smack in the middle of this... scorching hot "
"desert."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3597870895"
msgid "Bob:  Suddenly felt like I was on the sauce again, 'cept worse."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1665789405"
msgid "Bob:  Supposedly radiation from space would’ve cooked us otherwise."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1944517071"
msgid "Bob:  Sure you would. That's the problem."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/124055566"
msgid ""
"Bob:  Take it from a guy who’s been in his fair share of firefights -- having "
"someone who’s got your back is worth ALL the aggravation."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1882576846"
msgid ""
"Bob:  Thanks, doll. But honestly, I just didn’t want the headaches that come "
"with that job."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2251587347"
msgid ""
"Bob:  That didn’t exactly cheer her up, though I think she liked having "
"somewhere to lay flowers and remember her good buddy."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2945448167"
msgid "Bob:  That dragon-witch sure seemed glad I came along when I did..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/715599555"
msgid ""
"Bob:  That island was the first time I ever saw big, dumb lizards like Honker "
"here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/4022627645"
msgid ""
"Bob:  That was when he told me he missed Diana himself, even though they’d "
"been on opposite sides of the last world-war."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/37181434"
msgid ""
"Bob:  That’s just not how it works, Meeka. Look, maybe ol’ Uncle Bob here can "
"shed some light on the situation."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/4269214663"
msgid ""
"Bob:  That’s right, kid. As much as I like to take credit, your dad’s the "
"bona fide hero here. The real deal."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1110675774"
msgid "Bob:  That’s when ol’ Doc Rockwell showed up again."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2776702648"
msgid ""
"Bob:  That’s when the Witch piped up, to tell us it why it wasn’t worth "
"getting attached to no place there."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/4238526740"
msgid "Bob:  The Witch called it a ‘manti-corn’ -- or maybe a manti-clops?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/4132579752"
msgid "Bob:  The big guy seemed to have some real deep feelings after all."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1800771275"
msgid ""
"Bob:  The first world, I mean. Earth. Santiago’s told you about Earth, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2500332005"
msgid "Bob:  The guy got a little too curious for his own good..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3117194885"
msgid ""
"Bob:  The rest of ‘em scampered off, so I yelled to the ladies that it was "
"safe to come out."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3019226732"
msgid ""
"Bob:  Then again, after we all got to know each other better, there was "
"something between Diana and Santiago, too..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2091036345"
msgid ""
"Bob:  Things didn’t go exactly as planned, but we did manage to get into a "
"big, creepy lab with tanks full of sleeping animals."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2661106243"
msgid ""
"Bob:  Those jumped-up go-carts of his could really move! I mean I was hangin' "
"on for dear life, while Santiago laughed his butt off."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/4044579319"
msgid ""
"Bob:  Those red spotty ‘shrooms were bad news, but some of the others turned "
"out to be okay..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3418683261"
msgid ""
"Bob:  Those two seemed real close until this pilot from the future showed up. "
"Diana. And suddenly Helena was the odd one out."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/384190712"
msgid "Bob:  Thought I was done for when Humpty dropped dead on me..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1073768550"
msgid ""
"Bob:  To make a long, confusing story short: Little Miss Prof became all "
"super-powered using the ‘ARK Tek’, and decided to, uh..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3515384117"
msgid ""
"Bob:  Turned out her town needed a new sheriff, on account of the giant bugs "
"that kept attacking the place."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2338720504"
msgid ""
"Bob:  Turned out our Beast Queen had a whole squad of roughnecks from the "
"future backing her up."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3179632359"
msgid ""
"Bob:  Turned out she was right not to trust Doc Rockwell. He found some GOOP "
"deep down in the caves."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1931297970"
msgid "Bob:  Uh, Meeka -- listen, kid... these are just dumb stories."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3587033059"
msgid ""
"Bob:  Was probably an easier way to break the dumb beasts than smacking ‘em "
"upside the head and force-feeding ‘em..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/21073635"
msgid ""
"Bob:  Wasn’t easy, but Santiago and I eventually managed to fight our way "
"through that whole pack of freaks and open up the supply drop."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2790189098"
msgid ""
"Bob:  Wasn’t great finding out for sure we weren’t the original Bob or "
"Santiago."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3658591701"
msgid ""
"Bob:  Wasn’t long before your dad had a whole machine shop up and running, "
"where he could start putting together his new toys."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2725334693"
msgid "Bob:  We could barely keep up with the Beast Queen."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3757485571"
msgid ""
"Bob:  We covered your dad while he did his thing, but before we had a chance "
"to celebrate..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1706333881"
msgid ""
"Bob:  We fell for what seemed like forever. Turned out that pit had a bottom "
"after all."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3201536471"
msgid "Bob:  We got a message that something bad went down back at camp."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/4008747756"
msgid ""
"Bob:  We got there too late to save anybody. Everything was in ruins. And "
"there was no one around but ghosts."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/4099926817"
msgid "Bob:  We had our marching orders."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/716365442"
msgid ""
"Bob:  We hiked up ramp after ramp, until we must’ve been halfway to the sky."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/60636768"
msgid "Bob:  We just had to see what the local wildlife would eat."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/980503557"
msgid "Bob:  We were saying our goodbyes when that thing dropped in."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2236691813"
msgid "Bob:  We were sure glad we’d never have to deal with him again."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3695910718"
msgid ""
"Bob:  We weren’t sure yet how safe we were, even inside the city walls -- or "
"what was left of ‘em. So he sent us out in twos."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1732496414"
msgid "Bob:  Well now, I did have a little help from my friends."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2943967934"
msgid "Bob:  Well, I had SOME help."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3359422999"
msgid "Bob:  Well, I had SOME help..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1560850373"
msgid ""
"Bob:  Well, don’t you wanna hear about how me and your old man saved the "
"world?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2744159921"
msgid ""
"Bob:  Well, he used all the scrap and Tek we salvaged to build these "
"skyscraper-sized battle-bots. He called ‘em “Meks”."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2860196218"
msgid "Bob:  Well, no need for my name to even come up, is all I’m saying."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/261846172"
msgid ""
"Bob:  Well, that’s just the thing, kid. Nobody knows why we’re all here now "
"on this new world, when we were there before, on Earth."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/927396601"
msgid "Bob:  Well, there’s some folks who never find their people."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/71181613"
msgid ""
"Bob:  Well, with nothing much down there but rocks and fungus, we were gonna "
"need some luck."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3262475431"
msgid ""
"Bob:  Well, yeah... sure. In fact, you might say that I was the most "
"important part of the whole story."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/4022439900"
msgid ""
"Bob:  We’d never seen anything like it. Before we got back to camp, Santiago "
"pulled over and made me swear not to tell anyone yet."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/784149088"
msgid "Bob:  What are you drawing over there anyway?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1323970789"
msgid "Bob:  What are you drawing over there anyway?wing over there, anyway?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/910976594"
msgid "Bob:  What was left of the poor guy."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2966019441"
msgid ""
"Bob:  When the chips were down and things looked real bad, Santiago never. "
"Gave. An inch."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1284738626"
msgid ""
"Bob:  When we tried prying the thing open, it trapped us inside some kinda "
"force field, along with a bunch of the crazy local wildlife."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/295421052"
msgid "Bob:  Where was I? Oh yeah..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1166932243"
msgid ""
"Bob:  While we were watching, there was this loud noise, and something came "
"crashing down out in the wastes."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/576218375"
msgid "Bob:  Who knows? It’s all way beyond this G.I.’s pay-grade."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3788117420"
msgid "Bob:  Who’d have guessed something that big could even fly anyway?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3060961111"
msgid ""
"Bob:  Without warning, a sandstorm kicked up. I’m talking howling wind, "
"lightning."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/216595477"
msgid "Bob:  Wouldn’t you rather hear that story from the big guy himself?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3402294602"
msgid ""
"Bob:  Ya know, kid... sooner or later, you’re going to have to talk about it. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2979229569"
msgid "Bob:  Yeah well, just be glad you’re not gonna hear my ‘Helena’! "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1182868739"
msgid ""
"Bob:  Yeah, kid. It almost seems like some people are meant to meet up again."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/761333300"
msgid "Bob:  Yeah, those."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1691780770"
msgid ""
"Bob:  Yeah. He’s kinda the strong, silent type. No Jimmy Cagney, that’s for "
"sure."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3329755383"
msgid ""
"Bob:  Your dad did something that, uh, beamed us straight back to camp. But "
"we were still too late to save Diana."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/471174144"
msgid ""
"Bob:  Your dad was from the ‘right time’, but he and I saw up-close how that "
"crap wrecked the whole damn world!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3589581333"
msgid ""
"Bob:  Your old man got his war-wagon in gear, and kept his foot on the gas "
"until we were back inside the city walls."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3945174022"
msgid ""
"Bob:  Yup, and scampered off somewhere down in the dark, coward that he was..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2987114773"
msgid ""
"Bob:  ‘All terrain vehicles’, he called ‘em. Low-slung four-wheelers built "
"for speed -- and war."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3860178824"
msgid ""
"Bob:  ‘Cause he knew we weren’t gonna let him get away with what he’d done."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1871525552"
msgid ""
"Bob:  ‘Cause when I thought I saw a big whiskey jug sloshing around on six "
"legs, I sorta lost what was left of my pride."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/930950490"
msgid "Bob:  ‘Least I knew where to find water now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1067699292"
msgid "Bob:  ‘Specially that creepy cargo hold we found, full of clones."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3725836259"
msgid "Bob:  “Journey to the Center of the Broken ARK”"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2380140756"
msgid ""
"Bob:  “That slowed down before it landed. Supply drop, maybe? Let’s ‘Ride "
"Out’ and take it.”"
msgstr ""

