msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3885195518"
msgid ""
"Buried deep within this planet is the core of the seed ship that brought us "
"all here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1577494188"
msgid "BuriedTreasure"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/30283731"
msgid "Bury"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3315520792"
msgid "Bury is On Cooldown!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1278618081"
msgid "Busy building the modules..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3126545662"
msgid ""
"But Earth was the cradle of humanity, and Arat Prime remains its last "
"terrestrial outpost."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3305442024"
msgid "But I am no mere animal to be domesticated, nor preyed upon."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3309117000"
msgid "But I did know your mom -- a long, long time ago..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3202721624"
msgid "But I have no interest in starting over again on some"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3448471304"
msgid ""
"But I kept you from being turned by firing an Engram pulse through the ARK "
"Transmission Network."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3159355477"
msgid "But I promise, all in good time."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/4247061504"
msgid "But I think we’d be stronger together."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/4286195176"
msgid "But I think you understand,"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/160717614"
msgid ""
"But Meiyin’s story continued, to the far side of the Earth, into frozen "
"wastes shrouded in endless night..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2403192110"
msgid ""
"But Red Element is not comparable in power output to the blue substance, and "
"so the environmental pressures on our closed system of agriculture remain an "
"ongoing threat."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3221786600"
msgid ""
"But as I step over the ridgeline, I see the blood-red glow rising from the "
"great vista beyond "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/51138895"
msgid ""
"But before I tell you why, you have to promise this stays between you and I..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2326034992"
msgid "But everything in my head and my heart is telling me that..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1693921304"
msgid "But first, I think we both need a break."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1101330680"
msgid ""
"But for now, my team -- my people’s thoughts are with the brave crew of the "
"Genesis ship as they search the heavens for a new home for humanity."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1672539028"
msgid ""
"But for now, my team-- my people’s thoughts are with the brave crew of the "
"Genesis ship as they search the heavens for a new home for humanity."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/4173483542"
msgid "But for that to happen, I have to guide the one who will finish this."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2533725164"
msgid "But hang on... I’m detecting an opposing power-source nearby..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/59219211"
msgid "But her fate was my fault... I let her die..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/4048341275"
msgid "But how much longer can you afford to delay treatment? Hmm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/276543600"
msgid ""
"But if it’s a fight you want, my Master-Instructor and his Ossidon are about "
"to give you a final lesson."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/4016730577"
msgid "But if you did make it, it must have a use case..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/645844374"
msgid "But make no mistake, this is all thanks to you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3838385209"
msgid ""
"But now with the launch actually behind us, I find myself less comforted than "
"I had anticipated."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3274135711"
msgid "But once... it once had another name."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1508323564"
msgid "But should he not know that you are hearing voices?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3746001804"
msgid ""
"But the Queen’s affliction is a direct result of her unprovoked assault. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3066420623"
msgid "But the creature managed to leave one last copy of itself in that core."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2704777572"
msgid "But then"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/529050187"
msgid "But then there was so much torment. And the voices...!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/4244326874"
msgid "But there is no daylight to separate my delusions from rationality."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2568967247"
msgid ""
"But there’s still one place left on Earth where a form of Element still "
"lingers..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3459340422"
msgid "But they might just be guarding some high value treasure."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1688527339"
msgid ""
"But they will boost the outpost’s power supply, and that means more energy "
"for defenses!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1888370223"
msgid ""
"But we -- who labored for generations to preserve the biological riches of "
"planet Earth -- "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/4064474700"
msgid ""
"But what can I do to keep his forces at bay, and how long could I hold out "
"here at the fringes of his awareness?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2700238876"
msgid "But what little ‘Edmundium’ is to be found on this planet"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3827439500"
msgid "But what she found instead --"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1469839837"
msgid "But what she found instead--"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1358702379"
msgid "But whoever made it... they’re way beyond us."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3827262721"
msgid ""
"But why, unless... That’s who’s been helping you? Tell your Homo Deus friend "
"she can’t have it!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/781043849"
msgid "But yeah, this is serious."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2987359063"
msgid "But you remind me of someone from long ago, another true survivor..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1375334951"
msgid "But you seem to have a special way with dangerous animals."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3908155407"
msgid "But you will..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3779119685"
msgid ""
"But... they ARE always searching for ways in. Think they might be onto "
"something?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2300358818"
msgid "But... you’ve been with me for as long as I can remember. Guiding me..."
msgstr ""

