msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3344484523"
msgid "I"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1703132523"
msgid ""
"I -- I lashed out without thought... hurt allies, made mortal enemies of my "
"friends... She -- I killed her... I did it. Oh God..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2167205612"
msgid "I AGREE"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3613819649"
msgid "I Agree"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/4153022756"
msgid "I am a god."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2091434927"
msgid "I am going after Rockwell."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/522985868"
msgid ""
"I am quite generous to the deserving. This grotto once served as a retreat "
"for the most well-regarded of my lords and ladies."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3919643114"
msgid ""
"I am quite generous to the deserving. This grotto once served as a retreat "
"for the most well-regarded of my lords and ladies. Someone with your skills "
"could enjoy such favors, were you only more compliant."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2636435271"
msgid ""
"I am so tired of those miserable creatures plaguing my kingdom. Do not let "
"them have that outpost!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/325769036"
msgid "I am the hero here, not you!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1980668310"
msgid ""
"I am the reason you survived the slums of London, when they all set upon you "
"like a wounded dog."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3729154625"
msgid "I am you, Edmund. As you really are."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3234833647"
msgid "I assure you it does not."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3081428660"
msgid ""
"I began to realize that the failures of my first life need not define me "
"forever... great things were possible."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2567460785"
msgid "I believe myself quite capable of curing her affliction in short order."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2973611432"
msgid ""
"I breathe deeply. Then I take a step forward, and hope that this time, my "
"defenses will hold."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3498793794"
msgid ""
"I can almost glimpse a golden light behind it all, struggling to break "
"through that darkness."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1044062071"
msgid "I can almost..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/844967978"
msgid "I can handle my own emotions."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/847333732"
msgid "I can hear it so clearly now..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3983817036"
msgid "I can recall only shattered fragments of what came before."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3937845463"
msgid "I can see the world through my own eyes again."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2413810335"
msgid "I can sense a revenant horde approaching. Fortify while you can!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/22834956"
msgid "I can simply let them all go. Because with you... "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2594353706"
msgid ""
"I can't bear to see her like this... Please, Survivor, give it everything "
"you've got!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/248128223"
msgid ""
"I can't leave Meiyin alone, not again. There must be some way to lower her "
"defenses, and reach the person she was..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3726832719"
msgid "I chose life, and they love me for it!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3056412646"
msgid "I clearly overestimated you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1405274413"
msgid ""
"I could force her to my will, but that would crush my last hope of true "
"companionship."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/620743368"
msgid "I could only stun him for a moment."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3244945118"
msgid ""
"I could use some beauty sleep. Just hope Little Miss Prof’s right about this, "
"uh, prophecy of hers."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2476091389"
msgid ""
"I could use the beauty sleep. Just hope Little Miss Prof’s right about this, "
"uh, prophecy of hers."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1338183934"
msgid "I did love you... but you left me behind!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3573843345"
msgid "I did love you... but you left me behind... alone!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/325644095"
msgid ""
"I did not bother to rebuild while awaiting a diplomatic overture. And my "
"opponent did not keep me waiting long."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3960486384"
msgid "I did not pass his tests. His metal behemoths will march on without me,"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/785270274"
msgid ""
"I do feel it -- the reaper. She is coming to claim me. What can I do? I am "
"only one man, a weak man at that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3280351565"
msgid "I do not deny, "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3348931041"
msgid "I do. I loved someone once, very much..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/4015195739"
msgid "I don’t know that I was a hero. I just did what needed to be done."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2274370654"
msgid "I don’t know that I was a hero. I just did... what needed to be done."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/422451932"
msgid "I don’t know that there’s anyone like you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2442694743"
msgid "I don’t know. But it’s not death, Meiyin. It's..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3191732906"
msgid "I don’t love... I can’t love -- it’s a weakness. Get out of my head!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3336545261"
msgid "I expect those negotiations will be brief."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1530125345"
msgid ""
"I fall to my knees in the freezing wind. Better to let it end here, with some "
"semblance of humanity intact."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3126713199"
msgid "I fear our negotiations are off to a discouraging start."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1270214548"
msgid ""
"I feel myself finally slipping into nothingness, as it should be... And "
"then..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/513945393"
msgid "I had imagined far more of your humanity remained"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/4248236433"
msgid "I had to close this sanctuary because of the chaos you unleashed."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2119640056"
msgid ""
"I had to scuttle the seed ship to stop it from being overtaken by a terrible "
"monster."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/672732724"
msgid "I had to... leave her behind."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3292788763"
msgid "I have a friend that's working on it. It's just a matter of time."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3492298841"
msgid "I have seen your memories within the Codex."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2625488691"
msgid "I have... a galaxy to explore..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1344610185"
msgid ""
"I hear your voice first thing in the morning, and you sing me to sleep at "
"night."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3004902192"
msgid ""
"I hope in better times they will serve as a record of what has transpired "
"here... and what may yet come to be"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2526768750"
msgid ""
"I know it seems cruel -- believe me -- but you HAVE TO get to her while she’s "
"weakened."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/18823524"
msgid ""
"I know it seems cruel -- believe me -- but you have to get to her while she’s "
"weak."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3291817448"
msgid "I know you... Helena."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3899845832"
msgid "I know, dummy. Who do you think put the word in Santiago’s ear?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1705949594"
msgid "I know. And Meiyin... I’m scared."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1964247262"
msgid ""
"I lashed out without thought... hurt allies, made mortal enemies of my "
"friends... She -- I killed her... I did it. Oh God..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1413191090"
msgid "I left you once, Meiyin, but I won't this time."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1720326170"
msgid "I may be ‘The One Who Waits’, but I’m still Helena too."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3270106943"
msgid ""
"I must access the records of the ARK network to learn all I can about this "
"remarkable woman, and how she came to be here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1548664697"
msgid ""
"I must admit, I am curious: you have the technology to incarnate your minds"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3561861621"
msgid ""
"I must admit, I am glad that I coerced Miss Walker into accompanying me. Her "
"scientific mind may be far below my own, but she can fire a rifle "
"proficiently enough. I suppose that is no surprise. She is a colonial, after "
"all, and she never has been terribly ladylike. I hadn't noticed what a foul "
"mouth she has, either. Dreadful!\n"
"However, despite her past deceptions and uncouth vulgarity, I must tolerate "
"her presence for now. The predators here are not to be trifled with. Of "
"course, in my youth, I could have grappled them into submission. Why, I would "
"simply pin their wings behind their backs and drive them to the ground. Yes, "
"I'd give them a truly thorough thrashing!\n"
"Ah, to be young again... "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2190209410"
msgid "I must attend to my Queen just now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2697593250"
msgid ""
"I must escape this dark dominion before I fall prey to that terrible, "
"omnipresent will."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3475589047"
msgid "I must know -- who was it?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/323732029"
msgid "I need to ask you something,"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2112829062"
msgid ""
"I need you to recover and transmit the Codex -- our shared heritage -- so I "
"can use it to restore balance to my new world."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1476617594"
msgid "I never expected to see Helena again. We were... very close."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2475148651"
msgid "I promise your end will be anything but instant."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2884186696"
msgid "I promise... Auntie Helena."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1614308526"
msgid "I recognize... my ‘Edmundium’! Perhaps--"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1621908932"
msgid ""
"I remember everything now -- the struggles I faced, the losses I felt -- and "
"the love that I found."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3181995190"
msgid ""
"I remember. So many possibilities... I could be everywhere and everything."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3937572884"
msgid ""
"I see a daughter I could not save. My darling little girl, my little girl. "
"Lifeless. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3273953309"
msgid "I see foundries, forges, furnaces... but no foot soldiers."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1638147891"
msgid ""
"I see foundries, forges, furnaces... but no foot soldiers. Expect them to "
"defend their outpost from raiders with heavy armor and high explosives."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3316527683"
msgid "I should kill you for invading our refuge like this."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2013008757"
msgid ""
"I stumble about lost in Stygian darkness, raw flesh raked by an icy gale."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3399744272"
msgid "I suppose I have my answer."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1130622990"
msgid "I suppose now you know your limits."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2206459843"
msgid "I suspect we will not enjoy each other’s company."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2341089138"
msgid ""
"I swear I can’t seem to catch a break, Janie.\n"
"Almost threw in with some folks building Swiss Family Robinson-style houses "
"up in the trees. Getting above it all sure seemed like a great idea to me. "
"But then I couldn’t help noticing this outfit was gearing up for a fight.\n"
"It was like boot camp all over again, except I don’t remember any Chinese "
"lady sergeants there drilling recruits with pig-stickers. Besides, I wasn’t "
"keen about enlisting in a brand-new war so soon after I’d gone AWOL from "
"another.\n"
"So I struck out on my own, but not too far. Thought there might be something "
"to that safety in numbers idea, in case those guys from the mine came back to "
"make an example of us escapees. I spent a few days building a nice tree fort "
"all my own, off to one side of Toothpick Terraces.\n"
"No sooner did I have my place all set up just the way I liked, when the bad "
"guys showed up. I knew we were in for it when I saw they had artillery "
"mounted on dinosaurs. And sure enough, they started raining hell on us! All "
"that work for nothing...\n"
"In the middle of the mess I managed to spot the kid from the mine again, the "
"one who broke us out. You’d think I would have learned by now to stick with "
"her, but no. I heard her yelling to run into the swamps, and decided I might "
"do better going the opposite way.\n"
"\n"
"Already thinking I might’ve screwed up again -- BOB"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2527421619"
msgid ""
"I taught you the secrets of Edmundium in the violet caverns of that aberrant "
