msgctxt "GraphLiteral/157165433"
msgid ""
"Its population of mindless thralls bows under the yoke of a seemingly "
"omnipotent king."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/963182815"
msgid "Its roars will embolden nearby enemy forces until you bring it down!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/416996793"
msgid "It’s almost amusing to be judged by a walking anachronism."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/4268800301"
msgid ""
"It’s as if these two substances were inverse forces, one cancelling the other."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3271973721"
msgid ""
"It’s been over a thousand years since we last spoke, and I’m communicating "
"with you now from a distant planet..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/4210059833"
msgid "It’s coming for you, and quickly. What will you do?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2623359162"
msgid "It’s different with him from you and I, but it’s real too."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/443839426"
msgid "It’s finally begun. The ARKs are coming home."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/721221199"
msgid ""
"It’s hard to fully accept what we here at Arat Prime have accomplished "
"together, arguably the most momentous and audacious thing ever attempted by "
"human ingenuity."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2743540085"
msgid "It’s no use. My Sanguine Tek is self-repairing!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2060614658"
msgid "It’s no use. You’re losing."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1394998759"
msgid ""
"It’s not as if I am demanding the sacrifice of ensouled cognizant people to "
"feed our colony."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1626339393"
msgid "It’s not life either -- not exactly."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/679652833"
msgid "It’s nothing more than that. And I’ll always love you there."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2152713405"
msgid "It’s past time I gave you a history lesson."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3586959696"
msgid "It’s up to you to make sure their sacrifices weren’t in vain."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/645878096"
msgid "It’s weird -- almost feels like the Tek is meeting her halfway..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/676361770"
msgid "I’ll bet there are thermal pipes all over the city..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3246457799"
msgid ""
"I’ll do everything I can, but you’re going to need all the help you can "
"assemble for this assault."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1888796773"
msgid "I’m a man! Just a man... A father... a scientist... a friend..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/943272990"
msgid ""
"I’m afraid you’ve made a nuisance of yourself. A few of my special children "
"are on their way to convey my extreme disappointment."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3782767562"
msgid "I’m afraid..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1408531072"
msgid "I’m as giddy as an Etonian schoolboy."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1033803271"
msgid "I’m begging you... You have the strength... to let me go."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3653410752"
msgid "I’m just glad I got to see it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1193194010"
msgid "I’m not afraid."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/42208879"
msgid "I’m so glad we finally understand each other."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1181277117"
msgid "I’m so sorry, Meiyin. I could feel how close you two were..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1822115879"
msgid "I’m sorry Survivor, but there’s no time to catch your breath! "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3288786686"
msgid ""
"I’m sorry Survivor, but there’s no time to catch your breath! Inside to the "
"left, you’ve got a straight shot to the Codex -- but you’ve got to hurry!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/2240702484"
msgid "I’m sure you do."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/424421011"
msgid "I’m telling you, we’re both in!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/1885597542"
msgid "I’m the strength you used to escape predation on The Island."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3435849916"
msgid ""
"I’ve awoken surrounded by metallic wreckage, the bright thunderclap of my "
"arrival echoing away across a vast, rapidly-cooling crater."
