msgctxt "GraphLiteral/3200617647"
msgid ""
"Now Jane, before you get all wound up about me spending time with some "
"castaway girl, let me just say you got nothing to worry about on that score. "
"It’s more like when your folks used to make us take your know-it-all kid "
"sister along with us everywhere. You know -- a real pain in the ass.\n"
"She just washed up on my beach, and boy does it show! Doubt the girl would "
"last half a day on this island if I wasn’t here to babysit her. She's too "
"damn soft! The very first time I saw her, she kept me from catching some "
"squab for dinner.\n"
"And suddenly I’ve got some brat lecturing me about how her precious new pet’s "
"the last of its kind. Wants me to take her seriously, like she’s some kind of "
"expert. All she has to do is look around... I mean, those fat little birds "
"are all over the place here!\n"
"I haven’t even told you the nuttiest part, how she claims to be from the "
"FUTURE? At least she says the good guys won, which means you stayed safe and "
"sound stateside.\n"
"Either way, I thought I better show the girl what we’re dealing with here: "
"man-eating monsters, floating sky things, the whole nine yards. But maybe I "
"shouldn’t have rushed her. She’s been just staring at all of it, long enough "
"for me to take her picture and write you this note.\n"
"Don’t worry, I promise I won’t let her slow me down too much. Nothing’s "
"keeping me from getting back to your home cooking.\n"
"\n"
"Save me some, baby -- BOB"
msgstr ""

